nBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"540\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十四年十月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十四年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>晉侯夷吾卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"540\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":826,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129885","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00088","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯僖公二十五年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:09","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"541\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十五年正月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十五年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>二十有五年春，王正月，丙午，衛侯燬滅邢。<AlignEnd Key=\"541\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"542\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十五年四月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十五年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，癸酉，衛侯燬卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"542\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"543\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十五年四月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十五年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>宋蕩伯姬來逆婦。<AlignEnd Key=\"543\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"544\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十五年四月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十五年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>宋殺其大夫。<AlignEnd Key=\"544\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"545\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十五年七月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十五年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，楚人圍陳，納頓子于頓。<AlignEnd Key=\"545\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"546\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十五年七月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十五年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>葬衛文公。<AlignEnd Key=\"546\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"547\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十五年十二月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十五年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有二月，癸亥，公會衛子、莒慶盟于洮。<AlignEnd Key=\"547\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":827,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129886","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00089","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯僖公二十六年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"548\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十六年正月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十六年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>二十有六年春，王正月。<AlignEnd Key=\"548\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"549\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十六年正月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十六年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>己未，公會莒子、衛甯速盟于向。<AlignEnd Key=\"549\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"550\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十六年正月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十六年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>齊人侵我西鄙。<AlignEnd Key=\"550\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"551\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十六年正月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十六年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>公追齊師至酅，不及。<AlignEnd Key=\"551\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"552\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十六年四月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十六年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，齊人伐我北鄙。<AlignEnd Key=\"552\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"553\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十六年四月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十六年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>衛人伐齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"553\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"554\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十六年四月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十六年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>公子遂如楚乞師。<AlignEnd Key=\"554\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"555\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十六年七月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十六年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，楚人滅夔子歸。<AlignEnd Key=\"555\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"556\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十六年十月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十六年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，楚人伐宋，圍緡，公以楚師伐齊，取穀，公至自伐齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"556\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":828,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129887","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00090","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯僖公二十七年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"557\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十七年正月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十七年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，杞子來朝。<AlignEnd Key=\"557\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"558\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十七年六月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十七年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，六月，庚寅，齊侯昭卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"558\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"559\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十七年八月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十七年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月，乙未，葬齊孝公，乙巳，公子遂帥師入杞。<AlignEnd Key=\"559\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"560\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十七年null\" Term=\"魯僖公二十七年null\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，楚人，陳侯，蔡侯，鄭伯，許男，圍宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"560\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"561\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十七年十二月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十七年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，甲戌，公會諸侯盟于宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"561\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":829,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129888","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00091","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯僖公二十八年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"562\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十八年正月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十八年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，晉侯侵曹，晉侯伐衛。<AlignEnd Key=\"562\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"563\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十八年正月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十八年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>晉侯伐衛，公子買戍衛，不卒戍，刺之，楚人救衛。<AlignEnd Key=\"563\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"564\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十八年三月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十八年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，丙午，晉侯入曹，執曹伯，畀宋人。<AlignEnd Key=\"564\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"565\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十八年四月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十八年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，己巳，晉侯，齊師，宋師，秦師，及楚人戰于城濮，楚師敗績，楚殺其大夫得臣，衛侯出奔楚。<AlignEnd Key=\"565\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"566\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十八年五月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十八年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>五月，癸丑，公會晉侯，齊侯，宋公蔡侯，鄭伯，衛子，莒子，盟于踐土，陳侯如會，公朝于王所。<AlignEnd Key=\"566\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"567\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十八年六月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十八年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，衛侯鄭自楚復歸于衛，衛元咺出奔晉，陳侯款卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"567\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"568\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十八年七月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十八年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，杞伯姬來，公子遂如齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"568\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"569\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十八年十月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，公會晉侯，齊侯，宋公，蔡侯，鄭伯，陳子，莒子，邾人，秦人，于溫。<AlignEnd Key=\"569\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"570\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十八年十月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>天王狩于河陽，壬申，公朝于王所。<AlignEnd Key=\"570\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"571\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十八年十月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>晉人執衛侯歸之于京師，衛元咺自晉復歸于衛。<AlignEnd Key=\"571\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"572\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十八年十月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>諸侯遂圍許，曹伯襄復歸于曹，遂會諸侯圍許。<AlignEnd Key=\"572\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":830,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129889","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00092","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯僖公二十九年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"573\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十九年正月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十九年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>二十有九年，春，介葛盧來。公至自圍許。<AlignEnd Key=\"573\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"574\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十九年正月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十九年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>公至自圍許。<AlignEnd Key=\"574\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"575\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十九年六月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十九年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，六月，會王人，晉人，宋人，齊人，陳人，蔡人，秦人，盟于翟泉。<AlignEnd Key=\"575\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"576\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十九年七月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十九年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，大雨雹。<AlignEnd Key=\"576\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"577\" RefId=\"魯僖公二十九年十月\" Term=\"魯僖公二十九年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，介葛盧來。<AlignEnd Key=\"577\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":831,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129890","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00093","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯僖公三十年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"578\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十年正月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月。<AlignEnd Key=\"578\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"579\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十年四月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏\u2027狄侵齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"579\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"580\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十年七月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，衛殺其大夫元咺，及公子瑕，衛侯鄭歸于衛，晉人，秦人，圍鄭，介人侵蕭。<AlignEnd Key=\"580\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"581\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十年十月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，天王使宰周公來聘，公子遂如京師，遂如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"581\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":832,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129891","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00094","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯僖公三十一年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"582\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十一年正月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十一年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>三十有一年，春取濟西田。<AlignEnd Key=\"582\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"583\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十一年正月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十一年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>公子遂如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"583\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"584\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十一年四月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十一年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，四卜郊不從，乃免牲，猶三望。<AlignEnd Key=\"584\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"585\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十一年七月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十一年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月。<AlignEnd Key=\"585\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"586\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十一年十月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十一年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，杞伯姬來求婦，狄圍衛。<AlignEnd Key=\"586\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"587\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十一年十二月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十一年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，衛遷于帝丘。<AlignEnd Key=\"587\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":833,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129892","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00095","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯僖公三十二年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"588\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十二年正月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十二年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月。<AlignEnd Key=\"588\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"589\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十二年四月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十二年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，己丑，鄭伯捷卒，衛人侵狄。<AlignEnd Key=\"589\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"590\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十二年七月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十二年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，衛人及狄盟。<AlignEnd Key=\"590\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"591\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十二年十二月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十二年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有二月，己卯，晉侯重耳卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"591\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":834,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129893","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00096","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯僖公三十三年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"592\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十三年二月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十三年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王二月，秦人入滑。<AlignEnd Key=\"592\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"593\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十三年二月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十三年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>齊侯使國歸父來聘。<AlignEnd Key=\"593\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"594\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十三年四月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十三年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，辛巳，晉人及姜戎敗秦師于殽。<AlignEnd Key=\"594\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"595\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十三年四月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十三年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>癸巳，葬晉文公。<AlignEnd Key=\"595\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"596\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十三年四月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十三年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>狄侵齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"596\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"597\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十三年四月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十三年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>公伐邾，取訾婁。<AlignEnd Key=\"597\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"598\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十三年七月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十三年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，公子遂帥師伐邾。<AlignEnd Key=\"598\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"599\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十三年七月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十三年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>晉人敗狄于箕。<AlignEnd Key=\"599\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"600\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十三年十月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十三年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，公如齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"600\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"601\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十三年十二月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十三年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，公至自齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"601\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"602\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十三年十二月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十三年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>乙巳，公薨于小寢。<AlignEnd Key=\"602\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"603\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十三年十二月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十三年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>隕霜不殺草，李梅實。<AlignEnd Key=\"603\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"604\" RefId=\"魯僖公三十三年十二月\" Term=\"魯僖公三十三年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>晉人，陳人，鄭人，伐許。<AlignEnd Key=\"604\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":835,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129894","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00097","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯文公元年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"605\" RefId=\"魯文公元年正月\" Term=\"魯文公元年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公即位。<AlignEnd Key=\"605\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"606\" RefId=\"魯文公元年二月\" Term=\"魯文公元年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>二月，癸亥，日有食之。<AlignEnd Key=\"606\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"607\" RefId=\"魯文公元年二月\" Term=\"魯文公元年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>天王使叔服來會葬。<AlignEnd Key=\"607\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"608\" RefId=\"魯文公元年四月\" Term=\"魯文公元年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，丁巳，葬我君僖公。<AlignEnd Key=\"608\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"609\" RefId=\"魯文公元年四月\" Term=\"魯文公元年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>天王使毛伯來錫公命。<AlignEnd Key=\"609\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"610\" RefId=\"魯文公元年四月\" Term=\"魯文公元年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>晉侯伐衛。<AlignEnd Key=\"610\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"611\" RefId=\"魯文公元年四月\" Term=\"魯文公元年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>叔孫得臣如京師。<AlignEnd Key=\"611\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"612\" RefId=\"魯文公元年四月\" Term=\"魯文公元年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>衛人伐晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"612\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"613\" RefId=\"魯文公元年七月\" Term=\"魯文公元年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，公孫敖會晉侯于戚。<AlignEnd Key=\"613\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"614\" RefId=\"魯文公元年十月\" Term=\"魯文公元年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬十月，丁未，楚世子商臣弒其君頵。<AlignEnd Key=\"614\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"615\" RefId=\"魯文公元年十月\" Term=\"魯文公元年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>公孫敖如齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"615\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":836,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129895","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00098","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯文公二年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"616\" RefId=\"魯文公二年二月\" Term=\"魯文公二年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王二月，甲子，晉侯及秦師戰于彭衙，秦師敗績。<AlignEnd Key=\"616\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"617\" RefId=\"魯文公二年二月\" Term=\"魯文公二年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>丁丑，作僖公主。<AlignEnd Key=\"617\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"618\" RefId=\"魯文公二年三月\" Term=\"魯文公二年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，乙巳，及晉處父盟。<AlignEnd Key=\"618\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"619\" RefId=\"魯文公二年六月\" Term=\"魯文公二年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，六月，公孫敖會宋公，陳侯，鄭伯，晉士縠，盟于垂隴。<AlignEnd Key=\"619\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"620\" RefId=\"魯文公二年七月\" Term=\"魯文公二年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>自十有二月不雨，至于秋七月。<AlignEnd Key=\"620\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"621\" RefId=\"魯文公二年八月\" Term=\"魯文公二年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>八月，丁卯，大事于大廟，躋僖公。<AlignEnd Key=\"621\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"622\" RefId=\"魯文公二年十月\" Term=\"魯文公二年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，晉人，宋人，陳人，鄭人，伐秦。<AlignEnd Key=\"622\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"623\" RefId=\"魯文公二年十月\" Term=\"魯文公二年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>公子遂如齊納幣。<AlignEnd Key=\"623\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":837,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129896","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00099","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯文公三年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"624\" RefId=\"魯文公三年正月\" Term=\"魯文公三年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，叔孫得臣會晉人，宋人，陳人，衛人，鄭人，伐沈，沈潰。<AlignEnd Key=\"624\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"625\" RefId=\"魯文公三年五月\" Term=\"魯文公三年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月，王子虎卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"625\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"626\" RefId=\"魯文公三年五月\" Term=\"魯文公三年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>秦人伐晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"626\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"627\" RefId=\"魯文公三年七月\" Term=\"魯文公三年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，楚人圍江。<AlignEnd Key=\"627\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"628\" RefId=\"魯文公三年七月\" Term=\"魯文公三年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>雨螽于宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"628\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"629\" RefId=\"魯文公三年十月\" Term=\"魯文公三年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，公如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"629\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"630\" RefId=\"魯文公三年十二月\" Term=\"魯文公三年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，己巳，公及晉侯盟。<AlignEnd Key=\"630\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"631\" RefId=\"魯文公三年十二月\" Term=\"魯文公三年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>晉陽處父帥師伐楚，以救江。<AlignEnd Key=\"631\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":838,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129897","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00100","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯文公四年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"632\" RefId=\"魯文公四年正月\" Term=\"魯文公四年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，公至自晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"632\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"633\" RefId=\"魯文公四年四月\" Term=\"魯文公四年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，逆婦姜于齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"633\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"634\" RefId=\"魯文公四年四月\" Term=\"魯文公四年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>狄侵齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"634\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"635\" RefId=\"魯文公四年七月\" Term=\"魯文公四年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，楚人滅江。<AlignEnd Key=\"635\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"636\" RefId=\"魯文公四年七月\" Term=\"魯文公四年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>晉侯伐秦。<AlignEnd Key=\"636\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"637\" RefId=\"魯文公四年七月\" Term=\"魯文公四年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>衛侯使甯俞來聘。<AlignEnd Key=\"637\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"638\" RefId=\"魯文公四年十一月\" Term=\"魯文公四年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有一月，壬寅，夫人風氏薨。<AlignEnd Key=\"638\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":839,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129898","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00101","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯文公五年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"639\" RefId=\"魯文公五年正月\" Term=\"魯文公五年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，王使榮叔歸含，且賵。<AlignEnd Key=\"639\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"640\" RefId=\"魯文公五年三月\" Term=\"魯文公五年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，辛亥，葬我小君成風，王使召伯來會葬。<AlignEnd Key=\"640\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"641\" RefId=\"魯文公五年四月\" Term=\"魯文公五年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，公孫敖如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"641\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"642\" RefId=\"魯文公五年四月\" Term=\"魯文公五年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>秦人入鄀。<AlignEnd Key=\"642\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"643\" RefId=\"魯文公五年七月\" Term=\"魯文公五年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，楚人滅六。<AlignEnd Key=\"643\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"644\" RefId=\"魯文公五年十月\" Term=\"魯文公五年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，甲申，許男業卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"644\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":840,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129899","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00102","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯文公六年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"645\" RefId=\"魯文公六年正月\" Term=\"魯文公六年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，葬許僖公。<AlignEnd Key=\"645\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"646\" RefId=\"魯文公六年四月\" Term=\"魯文公六年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，季孫行父如陳。<AlignEnd Key=\"646\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"647\" RefId=\"魯文公六年七月\" Term=\"魯文公六年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，季孫行父如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"647\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"648\" RefId=\"魯文公六年八月\" Term=\"魯文公六年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>八月，乙亥，晉侯驩卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"648\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"649\" RefId=\"魯文公六年十月\" Term=\"魯文公六年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，公子遂如晉，葬晉襄公，晉殺其大夫陽處父。<AlignEnd Key=\"649\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"650\" RefId=\"魯文公六年十月\" Term=\"魯文公六年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>晉狐射姑出奔狄。<AlignEnd Key=\"650\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"651\" RefId=\"魯文公六年十月\" Term=\"魯文公六年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>閏月不告月，猶朝于廟。<AlignEnd Key=\"651\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":841,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129900","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00103","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯文公七年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"652\" RefId=\"魯文公七年正月\" Term=\"魯文公七年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>七年，春，公伐邾。<AlignEnd Key=\"652\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"653\" RefId=\"魯文公七年三月\" Term=\"魯文公七年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，甲戌，取須句，遂城郚。<AlignEnd Key=\"653\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"654\" RefId=\"魯文公七年四月\" Term=\"魯文公七年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，宋公王臣卒，宋人殺其大夫。<AlignEnd Key=\"654\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"655\" RefId=\"魯文公七年四月\" Term=\"魯文公七年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>戊子，晉人及秦人戰于令狐，晉先蔑奔秦，狄侵我西鄙。<AlignEnd Key=\"655\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"656\" RefId=\"魯文公七年八月\" Term=\"魯文公七年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月，公會諸侯，晉大夫，盟于扈。<AlignEnd Key=\"656\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"657\" RefId=\"魯文公七年十月\" Term=\"魯文公七年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，徐伐莒，公孫敖如莒蒞盟。<AlignEnd Key=\"657\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":842,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129901","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00104","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯文公八年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"658\" RefId=\"魯文公八年正月\" Term=\"魯文公八年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月。<AlignEnd Key=\"658\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"659\" RefId=\"魯文公八年四月\" Term=\"魯文公八年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月。<AlignEnd Key=\"659\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"660\" RefId=\"魯文公八年八月\" Term=\"魯文公八年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月，戊申，天王崩。<AlignEnd Key=\"660\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"661\" RefId=\"魯文公八年十月\" Term=\"魯文公八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，壬午，公子遂會晉趙盾，盟于衡雍。<AlignEnd Key=\"661\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"662\" RefId=\"魯文公八年十月\" Term=\"魯文公八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>乙酉，公子遂會雒戎，盟于暴<AlignEnd Key=\"662\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"663\" RefId=\"魯文公八年十月\" Term=\"魯文公八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>公孫敖如京師，不至而復，丙戌，奔莒<AlignEnd Key=\"663\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"664\" RefId=\"魯文公八年十月\" Term=\"魯文公八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>螽。<AlignEnd Key=\"664\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"665\" RefId=\"魯文公八年十月\" Term=\"魯文公八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>宋人殺其大夫司馬，宋司城來奔。<AlignEnd Key=\"665\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":843,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129902","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00105","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯文公九年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"666\" RefId=\"魯文公九年正月\" Term=\"魯文公九年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，毛伯來求金，夫人姜氏如齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"666\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"667\" RefId=\"魯文公九年二月\" Term=\"魯文公九年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>二月，叔孫得臣如京師，辛丑，葬襄王，晉人殺其大夫先都。<AlignEnd Key=\"667\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"668\" RefId=\"魯文公九年三月\" Term=\"魯文公九年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，夫人姜氏至自齊，晉人殺其大夫士縠，及箕鄭父，楚人伐鄭，公子遂會晉人，宋人，衛人，許人，救鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"668\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"669\" RefId=\"魯文公九年四月\" Term=\"魯文公九年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，狄侵齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"669\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"670\" RefId=\"魯文公九年八月\" Term=\"魯文公九年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月，曹伯襄卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"670\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"671\" RefId=\"魯文公九年九月\" Term=\"魯文公九年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，癸酉，地震。<AlignEnd Key=\"671\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"672\" RefId=\"魯文公九年十月\" Term=\"魯文公九年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，楚子使椒來聘，秦人來歸僖公成風之隧，葬曹共公。<AlignEnd Key=\"672\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":844,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129903","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00106","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯文公十年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"673\" RefId=\"魯文公十年三月\" Term=\"魯文公十年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>十年，春，王三月，辛卯，臧孫辰卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"673\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"674\" RefId=\"魯文公十年四月\" Term=\"魯文公十年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，秦伐晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"674\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"675\" RefId=\"魯文公十年四月\" Term=\"魯文公十年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>楚殺其大夫宜申。<AlignEnd Key=\"675\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"676\" RefId=\"魯文公十年四月\" Term=\"魯文公十年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>自正月不雨，至于秋。<AlignEnd Key=\"676\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"677\" RefId=\"魯文公十年四月\" Term=\"魯文公十年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>及蘇子盟于女栗。<AlignEnd Key=\"677\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"678\" RefId=\"魯文公十年十月\" Term=\"魯文公十年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，狄侵宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"678\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"679\" RefId=\"魯文公十年十月\" Term=\"魯文公十年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>楚子，蔡侯，次于厥貉。<AlignEnd Key=\"679\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":845,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129904","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00107","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯文公十一年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"680\" RefId=\"魯文公十一年正月\" Term=\"魯文公十一年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，楚子伐麇。<AlignEnd Key=\"680\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"681\" RefId=\"魯文公十一年四月\" Term=\"魯文公十一年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，叔仲彭生，會晉郤缺于承筐。<AlignEnd Key=\"681\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"682\" RefId=\"魯文公十一年七月\" Term=\"魯文公十一年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，曹伯來朝，公子遂如宋，狄侵齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"682\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"683\" RefId=\"魯文公十一年十月\" Term=\"魯文公十一年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，甲午，叔孫得臣敗狄于鹹。<AlignEnd Key=\"683\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":846,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129905","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00108","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯文公十二年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"684\" RefId=\"魯文公十二年正月\" Term=\"魯文公十二年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，郕伯來奔，杞伯來朝。<AlignEnd Key=\"684\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"685\" RefId=\"魯文公十二年二月\" Term=\"魯文公十二年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>二月，庚子，子叔姬卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"685\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"686\" RefId=\"魯文公十二年四月\" Term=\"魯文公十二年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，楚人圍巢。<AlignEnd Key=\"686\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"687\" RefId=\"魯文公十二年七月\" Term=\"魯文公十二年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，滕子來朝，秦伯使術來聘。<AlignEnd Key=\"687\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"688\" RefId=\"魯文公十二年十二月\" Term=\"魯文公十二年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有二月，戊午，晉人，秦人，戰于河曲。<AlignEnd Key=\"688\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"689\" RefId=\"魯文公十二年十二月\" Term=\"魯文公十二年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>季孫行父帥師，城諸及鄆。<AlignEnd Key=\"689\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":847,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129906","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00109","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯文公十三年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"690\" RefId=\"魯文公十三年正月\" Term=\"魯文公十三年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有三年，春，王正月。<AlignEnd Key=\"690\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"691\" RefId=\"魯文公十三年五月\" Term=\"魯文公十三年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月，壬午，陳侯朔卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"691\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"692\" RefId=\"魯文公十三年五月\" Term=\"魯文公十三年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>邾子蘧蒢卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"692\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"693\" RefId=\"魯文公十三年七月\" Term=\"魯文公十三年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>自正月不雨，至于秋七月，大室屋壞。<AlignEnd Key=\"693\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"694\" RefId=\"魯文公十三年十月\" Term=\"魯文公十三年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，公如晉，衛侯會公于沓。<AlignEnd Key=\"694\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"695\" RefId=\"魯文公十三年十月\" Term=\"魯文公十三年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>狄侵衛。<AlignEnd Key=\"695\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"696\" RefId=\"魯文公十三年十二月\" Term=\"魯文公十三年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，己丑，公及晉侯盟。<AlignEnd Key=\"696\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"697\" RefId=\"魯文公十三年十二月\" Term=\"魯文公十三年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>公還自晉，鄭伯會公于棐。<AlignEnd Key=\"697\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":848,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129907","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00110","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯文公十四年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"698\" RefId=\"魯文公十四年正月\" Term=\"魯文公十四年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公至自晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"698\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"699\" RefId=\"魯文公十四年正月\" Term=\"魯文公十四年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>邾人伐我南鄙，叔彭生帥帥伐邾。<AlignEnd Key=\"699\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"700\" RefId=\"魯文公十四年五月\" Term=\"魯文公十四年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月，乙亥，齊侯潘卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"700\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"701\" RefId=\"魯文公十四年六月\" Term=\"魯文公十四年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，公會宋公，陳侯，衛侯，鄭伯，許男，曹伯，晉趙盾，癸酉，同盟于新城。<AlignEnd Key=\"701\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"702\" RefId=\"魯文公十四年七月\" Term=\"魯文公十四年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，有星孛入于北斗。<AlignEnd Key=\"702\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"703\" RefId=\"魯文公十四年七月\" Term=\"魯文公十四年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>公至自會。<AlignEnd Key=\"703\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"704\" RefId=\"魯文公十四年七月\" Term=\"魯文公十四年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>晉人納捷菑于邾，弗克納。<AlignEnd Key=\"704\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"705\" RefId=\"魯文公十四年九月\" Term=\"魯文公十四年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，甲申，公孫敖卒于齊，齊公子商人弒其君舍。<AlignEnd Key=\"705\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"706\" RefId=\"魯文公十四年九月\" Term=\"魯文公十四年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>宋子哀來奔。<AlignEnd Key=\"706\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"707\" RefId=\"魯文公十四年十月\" Term=\"魯文公十四年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，單伯如齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"707\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"708\" RefId=\"魯文公十四年十月\" Term=\"魯文公十四年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>齊人執單伯。<AlignEnd Key=\"708\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"709\" RefId=\"魯文公十四年十月\" Term=\"魯文公十四年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>齊人執子叔姬。<AlignEnd Key=\"709\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":849,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129908","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00111","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯文公十五年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"710\" RefId=\"魯文公十五年正月\" Term=\"魯文公十五年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有五年，春，季孫行父如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"710\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"711\" RefId=\"魯文公十五年三月\" Term=\"魯文公十五年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，宋司馬華孫來盟。<AlignEnd Key=\"711\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"712\" RefId=\"魯文公十五年四月\" Term=\"魯文公十五年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，曹伯來朝。<AlignEnd Key=\"712\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"713\" RefId=\"魯文公十五年四月\" Term=\"魯文公十五年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>齊人歸公孫敖之喪。<AlignEnd Key=\"713\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"714\" RefId=\"魯文公十五年六月\" Term=\"魯文公十五年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，辛丑，朔，日有食之，鼓用牲于社。<AlignEnd Key=\"714\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"715\" RefId=\"魯文公十五年六月\" Term=\"魯文公十五年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>單伯至自齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"715\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"716\" RefId=\"魯文公十五年六月\" Term=\"魯文公十五年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>晉郤缺帥師伐蔡，戊申，入蔡。<AlignEnd Key=\"716\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"717\" RefId=\"魯文公十五年七月\" Term=\"魯文公十五年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，齊人侵我西鄙。<AlignEnd Key=\"717\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"718\" RefId=\"魯文公十五年七月\" Term=\"魯文公十五年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>季孫行父如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"718\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"719\" RefId=\"魯文公十五年十一月\" Term=\"魯文公十五年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有一月，諸侯盟于扈。<AlignEnd Key=\"719\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"720\" RefId=\"魯文公十五年十二月\" Term=\"魯文公十五年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，齊人來歸子叔姬，齊侯侵我西鄙，遂伐曹，入其郛。<AlignEnd Key=\"720\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":850,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129909","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00112","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯文公十六年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"721\" RefId=\"魯文公十六年正月\" Term=\"魯文公十六年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，季孫行父會齊侯于陽穀，齊侯弗及盟。<AlignEnd Key=\"721\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"722\" RefId=\"魯文公十六年五月\" Term=\"魯文公十六年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月，公四不視朔。<AlignEnd Key=\"722\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"723\" RefId=\"魯文公十六年六月\" Term=\"魯文公十六年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，戊辰，公子遂及齊侯，盟于郪丘。<AlignEnd Key=\"723\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"724\" RefId=\"魯文公十六年八月\" Term=\"魯文公十六年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月，辛未，夫人姜氏薨，毀泉臺，楚人，秦人，巴人，滅庸。<AlignEnd Key=\"724\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"725\" RefId=\"魯文公十六年八月\" Term=\"魯文公十六年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>毀泉臺，<AlignEnd Key=\"725\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"726\" RefId=\"魯文公十六年八月\" Term=\"魯文公十六年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>楚人，秦人，巴人，滅庸。<AlignEnd Key=\"726\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"727\" RefId=\"魯文公十六年十一月\" Term=\"魯文公十六年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有一月，宋人弒其君杵臼。<AlignEnd Key=\"727\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":851,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129910","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00113","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯文公十七年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"728\" RefId=\"魯文公十七年正月\" Term=\"魯文公十七年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，晉人，衛人，陳人，鄭人，伐宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"728\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"729\" RefId=\"魯文公十七年四月\" Term=\"魯文公十七年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，癸亥，葬我小君聲姜。<AlignEnd Key=\"729\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"730\" RefId=\"魯文公十七年四月\" Term=\"魯文公十七年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>齊侯伐我西鄙。<AlignEnd Key=\"730\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"731\" RefId=\"魯文公十七年六月\" Term=\"魯文公十七年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，癸未，公及齊侯盟于穀。<AlignEnd Key=\"731\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"732\" RefId=\"魯文公十七年六月\" Term=\"魯文公十七年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>諸侯會于扈。<AlignEnd Key=\"732\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"733\" RefId=\"魯文公十七年七月\" Term=\"魯文公十七年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，公至自穀。<AlignEnd Key=\"733\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"734\" RefId=\"魯文公十七年十月\" Term=\"魯文公十七年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，公子遂如齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"734\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":852,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129911","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00114","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯文公十八年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"735\" RefId=\"魯文公十八年二月\" Term=\"魯文公十八年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王二月，丁丑，公薨于臺下。<AlignEnd Key=\"735\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"736\" RefId=\"魯文公十八年二月\" Term=\"魯文公十八年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>秦伯罃卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"736\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"737\" RefId=\"魯文公十八年五月\" Term=\"魯文公十八年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月，戊戌，齊人弒其君商人。<AlignEnd Key=\"737\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"738\" RefId=\"魯文公十八年六月\" Term=\"魯文公十八年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，癸酉，葬我君文公。<AlignEnd Key=\"738\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"739\" RefId=\"魯文公十八年七月\" Term=\"魯文公十八年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，公子遂，叔孫得臣，如齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"739\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"740\" RefId=\"魯文公十八年十月\" Term=\"魯文公十八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，子卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"740\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"741\" RefId=\"魯文公十八年十月\" Term=\"魯文公十八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>夫人姜氏歸于齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"741\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"742\" RefId=\"魯文公十八年十月\" Term=\"魯文公十八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>季孫行父如齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"742\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"743\" RefId=\"魯文公十八年十月\" Term=\"魯文公十八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>莒弒其君庶其。<AlignEnd Key=\"743\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":853,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129912","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00115","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯宣公元年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"744\" RefId=\"魯宣公元年正月\" Term=\"魯宣公元年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公即位，公子遂如齊逆女。<AlignEnd Key=\"744\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"745\" RefId=\"魯宣公元年三月\" Term=\"魯宣公元年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，遂以夫人婦姜至自齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"745\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"746\" RefId=\"魯宣公元年四月\" Term=\"魯宣公元年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，季孫行父如齊，晉放其大夫胥甲父于衛，公會齊侯于平州，公子遂如齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"746\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"747\" RefId=\"魯宣公元年六月\" Term=\"魯宣公元年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，齊人取濟西田。<AlignEnd Key=\"747\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"748\" RefId=\"魯宣公元年七月\" Term=\"魯宣公元年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，邾子來朝，楚子，鄭人，侵陳，遂侵宋，晉趙盾帥師救陳，宋公，陳侯，衛侯，曹伯，會晉師于棐林，伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"748\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"749\" RefId=\"魯宣公元年十月\" Term=\"魯宣公元年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，晉趙穿帥師侵崇，晉人，宋人，伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"749\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":854,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129913","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00116","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯宣公二年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"750\" RefId=\"魯宣公二年二月\" Term=\"魯宣公二年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王二月，壬子，宋華元帥師，及鄭公子歸生帥師，戰于大棘，宋師敗績，獲宋華元，秦師伐晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"750\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"751\" RefId=\"魯宣公二年四月\" Term=\"魯宣公二年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏. 晉人，宋人，衛人，陳人，侵鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"751\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"752\" RefId=\"魯宣公二年九月\" Term=\"魯宣公二年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，九月，乙丑，晉趙盾弒其君夷皋。<AlignEnd Key=\"752\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"753\" RefId=\"魯宣公二年十月\" Term=\"魯宣公二年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，乙亥，天王崩。<AlignEnd Key=\"753\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":855,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129914","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00117","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯宣公三年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"754\" RefId=\"魯宣公三年正月\" Term=\"魯宣公三年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，郊牛之口傷，改卜牛，牛死，乃不郊，猶三望，葬匡王，楚子伐陸渾之戎。<AlignEnd Key=\"754\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"755\" RefId=\"魯宣公三年四月\" Term=\"魯宣公三年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，楚人侵鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"755\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"756\" RefId=\"魯宣公三年七月\" Term=\"魯宣公三年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，赤狄侵齊，宋師圍曹。<AlignEnd Key=\"756\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"757\" RefId=\"魯宣公三年十月\" Term=\"魯宣公三年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，丙戌，鄭伯蘭卒，葬鄭穆公。<AlignEnd Key=\"757\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":856,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129915","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00118","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯宣公四年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"758\" RefId=\"魯宣公四年正月\" Term=\"魯宣公四年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公及齊侯平莒及郯，莒人不肯，公伐莒，取向，秦伯稻卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"758\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"759\" RefId=\"魯宣公四年六月\" Term=\"魯宣公四年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，六月，乙酉，鄭公子歸生弒其君夷，赤狄侵齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"759\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"760\" RefId=\"魯宣公四年七月\" Term=\"魯宣公四年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，公如齊，公至自齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"760\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"761\" RefId=\"魯宣公四年十月\" Term=\"魯宣公四年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，楚子伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"761\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":857,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129916","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00119","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯宣公五年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"762\" RefId=\"魯宣公五年正月\" Term=\"魯宣公五年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，公如齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"762\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"763\" RefId=\"魯宣公五年四月\" Term=\"魯宣公五年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，公至自齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"763\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"764\" RefId=\"魯宣公五年九月\" Term=\"魯宣公五年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，九月，齊高固來逆叔姬，叔孫得臣卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"764\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"765\" RefId=\"魯宣公五年十月\" Term=\"魯宣公五年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，齊高固及子叔姬來，楚人伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"765\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":858,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129917","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00120","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯宣公六年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"766\" RefId=\"魯宣公六年正月\" Term=\"魯宣公六年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，晉趙盾，衛孫免，侵陳。<AlignEnd Key=\"766\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"767\" RefId=\"魯宣公六年四月\" Term=\"魯宣公六年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月。<AlignEnd Key=\"767\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"768\" RefId=\"魯宣公六年八月\" Term=\"魯宣公六年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月，螽。<AlignEnd Key=\"768\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"769\" RefId=\"魯宣公六年十月\" Term=\"魯宣公六年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月。<AlignEnd Key=\"769\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":859,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129918","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00121","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯宣公七年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"770\" RefId=\"魯宣公七年正月\" Term=\"魯宣公七年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，衛侯使孫良夫來盟。<AlignEnd Key=\"770\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"771\" RefId=\"魯宣公七年四月\" Term=\"魯宣公七年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，公會齊侯伐萊。<AlignEnd Key=\"771\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"772\" RefId=\"魯宣公七年七月\" Term=\"魯宣公七年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，公至自伐萊，大旱。<AlignEnd Key=\"772\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"773\" RefId=\"魯宣公七年十月\" Term=\"魯宣公七年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，公會晉侯，宋公，衛侯，鄭伯，曹伯，于黑壤。<AlignEnd Key=\"773\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":860,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129919","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00122","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯宣公八年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"774\" RefId=\"魯宣公八年正月\" Term=\"魯宣公八年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，公至自會。<AlignEnd Key=\"774\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"775\" RefId=\"魯宣公八年六月\" Term=\"魯宣公八年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，六月，公子遂如齊，至黃，乃復，辛巳，有事于大廟，仲遂卒于垂，壬午，猶繹，萬入，去籥，戊子，夫人嬴氏薨，晉師，白狄，伐秦，楚人滅舒蓼。<AlignEnd Key=\"775\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"776\" RefId=\"魯宣公八年七月\" Term=\"魯宣公八年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，甲子，日有食之，既。<AlignEnd Key=\"776\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"777\" RefId=\"魯宣公八年十月\" Term=\"魯宣公八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，己丑，葬我小君敬嬴，雨不克葬，庚寅，日中而克葬，城平陽，楚師伐陳。<AlignEnd Key=\"777\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":861,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129920","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00123","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯宣公九年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"778\" RefId=\"魯宣公九年正月\" Term=\"魯宣公九年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公如齊，公至自齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"778\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"779\" RefId=\"魯宣公九年四月\" Term=\"魯宣公九年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，仲孫蔑如京師，齊侯伐萊。<AlignEnd Key=\"779\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"780\" RefId=\"魯宣公九年七月\" Term=\"魯宣公九年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，取根牟。<AlignEnd Key=\"780\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"781\" RefId=\"魯宣公九年八月\" Term=\"魯宣公九年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>八月，滕子卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"781\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"782\" RefId=\"魯宣公九年九月\" Term=\"魯宣公九年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，晉侯，宋公，衛侯，鄭伯，曹伯，會于扈，晉荀林父帥師伐陳，辛酉，晉侯黑臀卒于扈。<AlignEnd Key=\"782\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"783\" RefId=\"魯宣公九年十月\" Term=\"魯宣公九年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，癸酉，衛侯鄭卒，宋人圍滕，楚子伐鄭，晉郤缺帥師救鄭，陳殺其大夫洩冶。<AlignEnd Key=\"783\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":862,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129921","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00124","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯宣公十年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"784\" RefId=\"魯宣公十年正月\" Term=\"魯宣公十年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，公如齊，公至自齊，齊人歸我濟西田。<AlignEnd Key=\"784\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"785\" RefId=\"魯宣公十年四月\" Term=\"魯宣公十年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，丙辰，日有食之，己巳，齊侯元卒，齊崔氏出奔衛，公如齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"785\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"786\" RefId=\"魯宣公十年五月\" Term=\"魯宣公十年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>五月，公至自齊，癸巳，陳夏徵舒弒其君平國。<AlignEnd Key=\"786\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"787\" RefId=\"魯宣公十年六月\" Term=\"魯宣公十年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，宋師伐滕，公孫歸父如齊，葬齊惠公，晉人，宋人，衛人，曹人，伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"787\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"788\" RefId=\"魯宣公十年七月\" Term=\"魯宣公十年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，天王使王季子來聘，公孫歸父帥師伐邾，取繹，大水，季孫行父如齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"788\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"789\" RefId=\"魯宣公十年十月\" Term=\"魯宣公十年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，公孫歸父如齊，齊侯使國佐來聘，饑，楚子伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"789\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":863,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129922","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00125","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯宣公十一年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"790\" RefId=\"魯宣公十一年正月\" Term=\"魯宣公十一年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月。<AlignEnd Key=\"790\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"791\" RefId=\"魯宣公十一年四月\" Term=\"魯宣公十一年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，楚子，陳侯，鄭伯，盟于辰陵，公孫歸父會齊人伐莒。<AlignEnd Key=\"791\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"792\" RefId=\"魯宣公十一年七月\" Term=\"魯宣公十一年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，晉侯會狄于欑函。<AlignEnd Key=\"792\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"793\" RefId=\"魯宣公十一年十月\" Term=\"魯宣公十一年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，楚人殺陳夏徵舒，丁亥，楚子入陳，納公孫寧儀行父于陳。<AlignEnd Key=\"793\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":864,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129923","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00126","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯宣公十二年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"794\" RefId=\"魯宣公十二年正月\" Term=\"魯宣公十二年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，葬陳靈公，楚子圍鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"794\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"795\" RefId=\"魯宣公十二年六月\" Term=\"魯宣公十二年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，六月，乙卯，晉荀林父帥師及楚子戰于邲，晉師敗績。<AlignEnd Key=\"795\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"796\" RefId=\"魯宣公十二年七月\" Term=\"魯宣公十二年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月。<AlignEnd Key=\"796\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"797\" RefId=\"魯宣公十二年十二月\" Term=\"魯宣公十二年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有二月，戊寅，楚子滅蕭，晉人，宋人，衛人，曹人，同盟于清丘，宋師伐陳，衛人救陳。<AlignEnd Key=\"797\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":865,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129924","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00127","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯宣公十三年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"798\" RefId=\"魯宣公十三年正月\" Term=\"魯宣公十三年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，齊師伐莒。<AlignEnd Key=\"798\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"799\" RefId=\"魯宣公十三年四月\" Term=\"魯宣公十三年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，楚子伐宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"799\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"800\" RefId=\"魯宣公十三年七月\" Term=\"魯宣公十三年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，螽。<AlignEnd Key=\"800\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"801\" RefId=\"魯宣公十三年十月\" Term=\"魯宣公十三年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，晉殺其大夫先縠。<AlignEnd Key=\"801\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":866,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129925","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00128","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯宣公十四年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"802\" RefId=\"魯宣公十四年正月\" Term=\"魯宣公十四年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，衛殺其大夫孔達。<AlignEnd Key=\"802\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"803\" RefId=\"魯宣公十四年五月\" Term=\"魯宣公十四年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月，壬申，曹伯壽卒，晉侯伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"803\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"804\" RefId=\"魯宣公十四年九月\" Term=\"魯宣公十四年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，九月，楚子圍宋，葬曹文公。<AlignEnd Key=\"804\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"805\" RefId=\"魯宣公十四年十月\" Term=\"魯宣公十四年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，公孫歸父會齊侯于穀。<AlignEnd Key=\"805\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":867,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129926","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00129","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯宣公十五年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"806\" RefId=\"魯宣公十五年正月\" Term=\"魯宣公十五年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，公孫歸父會楚子于宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"806\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"807\" RefId=\"魯宣公十五年五月\" Term=\"魯宣公十五年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月，宋人及楚人平。<AlignEnd Key=\"807\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"808\" RefId=\"魯宣公十五年六月\" Term=\"魯宣公十五年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，癸卯，晉師滅赤狄潞氏，以潞子嬰兒歸，秦人伐晉，王札子殺召伯，毛伯。<AlignEnd Key=\"808\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"809\" RefId=\"魯宣公十五年七月\" Term=\"魯宣公十五年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋\u2027螽，仲孫蔑，會齊高固于無婁，初稅畝。<AlignEnd Key=\"809\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"810\" RefId=\"魯宣公十五年十月\" Term=\"魯宣公十五年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，蝝生，饑。<AlignEnd Key=\"810\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":868,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129927","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00130","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯宣公十六年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"811\" RefId=\"魯宣公十六年正月\" Term=\"魯宣公十六年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，晉人滅赤狄甲氏，及留吁。<AlignEnd Key=\"811\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"812\" RefId=\"魯宣公十六年四月\" Term=\"魯宣公十六年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，成周宣榭火。<AlignEnd Key=\"812\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"813\" RefId=\"魯宣公十六年七月\" Term=\"魯宣公十六年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，郯伯姬來歸。<AlignEnd Key=\"813\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"814\" RefId=\"魯宣公十六年十月\" Term=\"魯宣公十六年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，大有年。<AlignEnd Key=\"814\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":869,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129928","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00131","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯宣公十七年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"815\" RefId=\"魯宣公十七年正月\" Term=\"魯宣公十七年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，庚子，許男錫我卒，丁未，蔡侯申卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"815\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"816\" RefId=\"魯宣公十七年四月\" Term=\"魯宣公十七年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，葬許昭公，葬蔡文公。<AlignEnd Key=\"816\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"817\" RefId=\"魯宣公十七年六月\" Term=\"魯宣公十七年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，癸卯，日有食之，己未，公會晉侯，衛侯，曹伯，邾子，同盟于斷道。<AlignEnd Key=\"817\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"818\" RefId=\"魯宣公十七年七月\" Term=\"魯宣公十七年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，公至自會。<AlignEnd Key=\"818\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"819\" RefId=\"魯宣公十七年十一月\" Term=\"魯宣公十七年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有一月，壬午，公弟叔肸卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"819\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":870,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129929","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00132","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯宣公十八年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"820\" RefId=\"魯宣公十八年正月\" Term=\"魯宣公十八年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，晉侯，衛世子臧，伐齊，公伐杞。<AlignEnd Key=\"820\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"821\" RefId=\"魯宣公十八年四月\" Term=\"魯宣公十八年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月。<AlignEnd Key=\"821\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"822\" RefId=\"魯宣公十八年七月\" Term=\"魯宣公十八年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，邾人戕鄫子于鄫，甲戌，楚子旅卒，公孫歸父如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"822\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"823\" RefId=\"魯宣公十八年十月\" Term=\"魯宣公十八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，壬戌，公薨于路寢，歸父還自晉，至笙，遂奔齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"823\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":871,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129930","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00133","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯成公元年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"824\" RefId=\"魯成公元年正月\" Term=\"魯成公元年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公即位。<AlignEnd Key=\"824\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"825\" RefId=\"魯成公元年二月\" Term=\"魯成公元年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>二月，辛酉，葬我君宣公，無冰。<AlignEnd Key=\"825\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"826\" RefId=\"魯成公元年三月\" Term=\"魯成公元年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，作丘甲。<AlignEnd Key=\"826\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"827\" RefId=\"魯成公元年四月\" Term=\"魯成公元年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，臧孫許，及晉侯，盟于赤棘。<AlignEnd Key=\"827\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"828\" RefId=\"魯成公元年七月\" Term=\"魯成公元年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，王師敗績于茅戎。<AlignEnd Key=\"828\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"829\" RefId=\"魯成公元年十月\" Term=\"魯成公元年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月。<AlignEnd Key=\"829\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":872,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129931","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00134","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯成公二年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"830\" RefId=\"魯成公二年正月\" Term=\"魯成公二年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，齊侯伐我北鄙。<AlignEnd Key=\"830\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"831\" RefId=\"魯成公二年四月\" Term=\"魯成公二年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，丙戌，衛孫良夫帥師，及齊師戰于新築，衛師敗績。<AlignEnd Key=\"831\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"832\" RefId=\"魯成公二年六月\" Term=\"魯成公二年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，癸酉，季孫行父，臧孫許，叔孫僑如，公孫嬰齊，帥師會晉郤克，衛孫良夫，曹公子首，及齊侯戰于鞍，齊師敗績。<AlignEnd Key=\"832\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"833\" RefId=\"魯成公二年七月\" Term=\"魯成公二年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，齊侯使國佐如師，己酉，及國佐盟于袁婁。<AlignEnd Key=\"833\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"834\" RefId=\"魯成公二年八月\" Term=\"魯成公二年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>八月，壬午，宋公鮑卒，庚寅，衛侯速卒，取汶陽田。<AlignEnd Key=\"834\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"835\" RefId=\"魯成公二年十月\" Term=\"魯成公二年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，楚師，鄭師，侵衛。<AlignEnd Key=\"835\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"836\" RefId=\"魯成公二年十一月\" Term=\"魯成公二年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有一月，公會楚公子嬰齊于蜀，丙申，公及楚人，秦人，宋人，陳人，衛人，鄭人，齊人，曹人，邾人，薛人，鄫人，盟于蜀。<AlignEnd Key=\"836\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":873,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129932","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00135","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯成公三年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"837\" RefId=\"魯成公三年正月\" Term=\"魯成公三年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公會晉侯，宋公，衛侯，曹伯，伐鄭，辛亥，葬衛穆公。<AlignEnd Key=\"837\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"838\" RefId=\"魯成公三年二月\" Term=\"魯成公三年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>二月，公至自伐鄭，甲子，新宮災，三日哭，乙亥，葬宋文公。<AlignEnd Key=\"838\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"839\" RefId=\"魯成公三年四月\" Term=\"魯成公三年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，公如晉，鄭公子去疾帥師伐許，公至自晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"839\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"840\" RefId=\"魯成公三年七月\" Term=\"魯成公三年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，叔孫僑如帥師圍棘，大雩，晉郤克，衛孫良夫，伐廧咎如。<AlignEnd Key=\"840\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"841\" RefId=\"魯成公三年十一月\" Term=\"魯成公三年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有一月，晉侯使荀庚來聘，衛侯使孫良夫來聘，丙午，及荀庚盟，丁未，及孫良夫盟，鄭伐許。<AlignEnd Key=\"841\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":874,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129933","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00136","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯成公四年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"842\" RefId=\"魯成公四年正月\" Term=\"魯成公四年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，宋公使華元來聘。<AlignEnd Key=\"842\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"843\" RefId=\"魯成公四年三月\" Term=\"魯成公四年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，壬申，鄭伯堅卒，杞伯來朝。<AlignEnd Key=\"843\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"844\" RefId=\"魯成公四年四月\" Term=\"魯成公四年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，甲寅，臧孫許卒，公如晉，葬鄭襄公。<AlignEnd Key=\"844\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"845\" RefId=\"魯成公四年七月\" Term=\"魯成公四年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，公至自晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"845\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"846\" RefId=\"魯成公四年十月\" Term=\"魯成公四年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，城鄆，鄭伯伐許。<AlignEnd Key=\"846\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":875,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129934","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00137","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯成公五年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"847\" RefId=\"魯成公五年正月\" Term=\"魯成公五年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，杞叔姬來歸，仲孫蔑如宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"847\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"848\" RefId=\"魯成公五年四月\" Term=\"魯成公五年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，叔孫僑如會晉荀首于穀，梁山崩。<AlignEnd Key=\"848\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"849\" RefId=\"魯成公五年七月\" Term=\"魯成公五年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，大水。<AlignEnd Key=\"849\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"850\" RefId=\"魯成公五年十一月\" Term=\"魯成公五年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有一月，己酉，天王崩。<AlignEnd Key=\"850\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"851\" RefId=\"魯成公五年十二月\" Term=\"魯成公五年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，己丑，公會晉侯，齊侯，宋公，衛侯，鄭伯，曹伯，邾子，杞伯，同盟于蟲牢。<AlignEnd Key=\"851\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":876,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129935","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00138","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯成公六年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"852\" RefId=\"魯成公六年正月\" Term=\"魯成公六年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公至自會。<AlignEnd Key=\"852\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"853\" RefId=\"魯成公六年二月\" Term=\"魯成公六年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>二月，辛巳，立武宮，取鄟，衛孫良夫帥師侵宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"853\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"854\" RefId=\"魯成公六年六月\" Term=\"魯成公六年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，六月，邾子來朝，公孫嬰齊如晉，壬申，鄭伯費卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"854\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"855\" RefId=\"魯成公六年七月\" Term=\"魯成公六年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，仲孫蔑，叔孫僑如，帥師侵宋，楚公子嬰齊帥師伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"855\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"856\" RefId=\"魯成公六年十月\" Term=\"魯成公六年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，季孫行父如晉，晉欒書帥師救鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"856\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":877,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129936","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00139","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯成公七年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"857\" RefId=\"魯成公七年正月\" Term=\"魯成公七年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，鼷鼠食郊牛角，改卜牛，鼷鼠又食其角，乃免牛，吳伐郯。<AlignEnd Key=\"857\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"858\" RefId=\"魯成公七年五月\" Term=\"魯成公七年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月，曹伯來朝，不郊猶三望。<AlignEnd Key=\"858\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"859\" RefId=\"魯成公七年七月\" Term=\"魯成公七年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，楚公子嬰齊帥師伐鄭，公會晉侯，齊侯，宋公，衛侯，曹伯，莒子，邾子，杞伯，救鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"859\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"860\" RefId=\"魯成公七年八月\" Term=\"魯成公七年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>八月，戊辰，同盟于馬陵，公至自會，吳入州來。<AlignEnd Key=\"860\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"861\" RefId=\"魯成公七年十月\" Term=\"魯成公七年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，大雩，衛孫林父出奔晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"861\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":878,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129937","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00140","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯成公八年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"862\" RefId=\"魯成公八年正月\" Term=\"魯成公八年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，晉侯使韓穿來言汶陽之田，歸之于齊，晉欒書帥師侵蔡，公孫嬰齊如莒，宋公使華元來聘。<AlignEnd Key=\"862\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"863\" RefId=\"魯成公八年四月\" Term=\"魯成公八年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，宋公使公孫壽來納幣，晉殺其大夫趙同，趙括。<AlignEnd Key=\"863\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"864\" RefId=\"魯成公八年七月\" Term=\"魯成公八年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，天子使召伯來賜公命。<AlignEnd Key=\"864\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"865\" RefId=\"魯成公八年十月\" Term=\"魯成公八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，癸卯，杞叔姬卒，晉侯使士燮來聘，叔孫僑如會晉士燮，齊人，邾人，伐剡，衛人來媵。<AlignEnd Key=\"865\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":879,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129938","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00141","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯成公九年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"866\" RefId=\"魯成公九年正月\" Term=\"魯成公九年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，杞伯來逆叔姬之喪以歸，公會晉侯，齊侯，宋公，衛侯，鄭伯，曹伯，莒子，杞伯，同盟于蒲，公至自會。<AlignEnd Key=\"866\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"867\" RefId=\"魯成公九年二月\" Term=\"魯成公九年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>二月，伯姬歸于宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"867\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"868\" RefId=\"魯成公九年四月\" Term=\"魯成公九年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，季孫行父如宋致女，晉人來媵。<AlignEnd Key=\"868\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"869\" RefId=\"魯成公九年七月\" Term=\"魯成公九年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，丙子，齊侯無野卒，晉人執鄭伯，晉欒書帥師伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"869\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"870\" RefId=\"魯成公九年十一月\" Term=\"魯成公九年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有一月，葬齊頃公，楚公子嬰齊帥師伐莒，庚申，莒潰，楚人入鄆，秦人白狄伐晉，鄭人圍許，城中城。<AlignEnd Key=\"870\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":880,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129939","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00142","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯成公十年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"871\" RefId=\"魯成公十年正月\" Term=\"魯成公十年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，衛侯之弟黑背，帥師侵鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"871\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"872\" RefId=\"魯成公十年四月\" Term=\"魯成公十年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，五卜郊不從，乃不郊。<AlignEnd Key=\"872\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"873\" RefId=\"魯成公十年五月\" Term=\"魯成公十年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>五月，公會晉侯，齊侯，宋公，衛侯，曹伯，伐鄭，齊人來媵，丙午，晉侯獳卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"873\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"874\" RefId=\"魯成公十年七月\" Term=\"魯成公十年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，公如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"874\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"875\" RefId=\"魯成公十年十月\" Term=\"魯成公十年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月。<AlignEnd Key=\"875\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":881,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129940","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00143","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯成公十一年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"876\" RefId=\"魯成公十一年三月\" Term=\"魯成公十一年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王三月，公至自晉，晉侯使郤犨來聘，己丑，及郤犨盟。<AlignEnd Key=\"876\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"877\" RefId=\"魯成公十一年四月\" Term=\"魯成公十一年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，季孫行父如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"877\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"878\" RefId=\"魯成公十一年七月\" Term=\"魯成公十一年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，叔孫僑如如齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"878\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"879\" RefId=\"魯成公十一年十月\" Term=\"魯成公十一年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月。<AlignEnd Key=\"879\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":882,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129941","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00144","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯成公十二年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"880\" RefId=\"魯成公十二年正月\" Term=\"魯成公十二年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，周公出奔晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"880\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"881\" RefId=\"魯成公十二年四月\" Term=\"魯成公十二年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，公會晉侯，衛侯，于瑣澤。<AlignEnd Key=\"881\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"882\" RefId=\"魯成公十二年七月\" Term=\"魯成公十二年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，晉人敗狄于交剛。<AlignEnd Key=\"882\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"883\" RefId=\"魯成公十二年十月\" Term=\"魯成公十二年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月。<AlignEnd Key=\"883\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":883,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129942","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00145","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯成公十三年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"884\" RefId=\"魯成公十三年三月\" Term=\"魯成公十三年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，晉侯使郤錡來乞師， 三月，公如京師，公。<AlignEnd Key=\"884\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"885\" RefId=\"魯成公十三年五月\" Term=\"魯成公十三年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>五月，公自京師，遂會晉侯，齊侯，宋公，衛侯，鄭伯，曹伯，邾人，滕人，伐秦，曹伯盧卒于師。<AlignEnd Key=\"885\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"886\" RefId=\"魯成公十三年七月\" Term=\"魯成公十三年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，公至自伐秦。<AlignEnd Key=\"886\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"887\" RefId=\"魯成公十三年十月\" Term=\"魯成公十三年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，葬曹宣公。<AlignEnd Key=\"887\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":884,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129943","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00146","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯成公十四年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"888\" RefId=\"魯成公十四年正月\" Term=\"魯成公十四年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，莒子朱卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"888\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"889\" RefId=\"魯成公十四年四月\" Term=\"魯成公十四年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，衛孫林父自晉歸于衛。<AlignEnd Key=\"889\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"890\" RefId=\"魯成公十四年七月\" Term=\"魯成公十四年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，叔孫僑如如齊逆女，鄭公子喜帥師伐許。<AlignEnd Key=\"890\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"891\" RefId=\"魯成公十四年九月\" Term=\"魯成公十四年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，僑如以夫人婦姜氏至自齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"891\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"892\" RefId=\"魯成公十四年十月\" Term=\"魯成公十四年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，庚寅，衛侯臧卒，秦伯卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"892\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":885,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129944","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00147","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯成公十五年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"893\" RefId=\"魯成公十五年二月\" Term=\"魯成公十五年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王二月，葬衛定公。<AlignEnd Key=\"893\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"894\" RefId=\"魯成公十五年三月\" Term=\"魯成公十五年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，乙巳，仲嬰齊卒，癸丑，公會晉侯，衛侯，鄭伯，曹伯，宋世子成，齊國佐，邾人，同盟于戚，晉侯執曹伯，歸于京師，公至自會。<AlignEnd Key=\"894\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"895\" RefId=\"魯成公十五年六月\" Term=\"魯成公十五年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，六月，宋公固卒，楚子伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"895\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"896\" RefId=\"魯成公十五年八月\" Term=\"魯成公十五年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月，庚辰，葬宋共公，宋華元，出奔晉，宋華元自晉歸于宋，宋殺其大夫山，宋魚石出奔楚。<AlignEnd Key=\"896\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"897\" RefId=\"魯成公十五年十一月\" Term=\"魯成公十五年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有一月，叔孫僑如會晉士燮，齊高無咎，宋華元，衛孫林父，鄭公子\u9c0c，邾人，會吳于鍾離，許遷于葉。<AlignEnd Key=\"897\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":886,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129945","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00148","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯成公十六年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:10","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"898\" RefId=\"魯成公十六年正月\" Term=\"魯成公十六年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，雨木冰。<AlignEnd Key=\"898\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"899\" RefId=\"魯成公十六年四月\" Term=\"魯成公十六年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，辛未，滕子卒，鄭公子喜帥師侵宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"899\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"900\" RefId=\"魯成公十六年六月\" Term=\"魯成公十六年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，丙寅朔，日有食之，晉侯使欒黶來乞師，甲午，晦，晉侯及楚子，鄭伯，戰于鄢陵，楚子鄭師敗績，楚殺其大夫公子側。<AlignEnd Key=\"900\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"901\" RefId=\"魯成公十六年七月\" Term=\"魯成公十六年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，公會晉侯，齊侯，衛侯，宋華元，邾人，于沙隨，不見公，公至自會，公會尹子，晉侯，齊國佐，邾人，伐鄭，曹伯歸自京師。<AlignEnd Key=\"901\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"902\" RefId=\"魯成公十六年九月\" Term=\"魯成公十六年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，晉人執季孫行父，舍之于苕丘。<AlignEnd Key=\"902\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"903\" RefId=\"魯成公十六年十月\" Term=\"魯成公十六年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，乙亥，叔孫僑如出奔齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"903\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"904\" RefId=\"魯成公十六年十二月\" Term=\"魯成公十六年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，乙丑，季孫行父及晉郤犨盟于扈，公至自會，乙酉，刺公子偃。<AlignEnd Key=\"904\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":887,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129946","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00149","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯成公十七年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"905\" RefId=\"魯成公十七年正月\" Term=\"魯成公十七年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，衛北宮括帥師侵鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"905\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"906\" RefId=\"魯成公十七年四月\" Term=\"魯成公十七年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，公會尹子，單子，晉侯，齊侯，宋公，衛侯，曹伯，邾人，伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"906\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"907\" RefId=\"魯成公十七年六月\" Term=\"魯成公十七年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，乙酉，同盟于柯陵。<AlignEnd Key=\"907\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"908\" RefId=\"魯成公十七年七月\" Term=\"魯成公十七年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，公至自會，齊高無咎出奔莒。<AlignEnd Key=\"908\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"909\" RefId=\"魯成公十七年九月\" Term=\"魯成公十七年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，辛丑，用郊，晉侯使荀罃來乞師。<AlignEnd Key=\"909\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"910\" RefId=\"魯成公十七年十月\" Term=\"魯成公十七年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，公會單子，晉侯，宋公，衛侯，曹伯，齊人，邾人，伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"910\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"911\" RefId=\"魯成公十七年十一月\" Term=\"魯成公十七年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有一月，公至自伐鄭，壬申，公孫嬰卒于貍脤。<AlignEnd Key=\"911\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"912\" RefId=\"魯成公十七年十二月\" Term=\"魯成公十七年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月丁已朔，日有食之，邾子貜且卒，晉殺其大夫郤錡，郤犨，郤至，楚人滅舒庸。<AlignEnd Key=\"912\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":888,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129947","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00150","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯成公十八年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"913\" RefId=\"魯成公十八年正月\" Term=\"魯成公十八年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，晉殺其大夫胥童，庚申，晉弒其君州蒲，齊殺其大夫國佐，公如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"913\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"914\" RefId=\"魯成公十八年四月\" Term=\"魯成公十八年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，楚子，鄭伯，伐宋，宋魚石復入于彭城，公至自晉，晉侯使士\u5304來聘。<AlignEnd Key=\"914\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"915\" RefId=\"魯成公十八年七月\" Term=\"魯成公十八年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，杞伯來朝。<AlignEnd Key=\"915\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"916\" RefId=\"魯成公十八年八月\" Term=\"魯成公十八年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>八月，邾子來朝，築鹿囿，己丑，公薨于路寢。<AlignEnd Key=\"916\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"917\" RefId=\"魯成公十八年十月\" Term=\"魯成公十八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，楚人鄭人侵宋，晉侯使士魴來乞師。<AlignEnd Key=\"917\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"918\" RefId=\"魯成公十八年十二月\" Term=\"魯成公十八年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，仲孫蔑會晉侯，宋公，衛侯，邾子，齊崔杼，同盟于虛朾，丁未，葬我君成公。<AlignEnd Key=\"918\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":889,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129948","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00151","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公元年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"919\" RefId=\"魯襄公元年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公元年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公即位，仲孫蔑會晉欒黶，宋華元，衛甯殖，曹人，莒人，邾人，滕人，宋人，薛人，圍宋彭城。<AlignEnd Key=\"919\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"920\" RefId=\"魯襄公元年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公元年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，晉韓厥帥師伐鄭，仲孫蔑會齊崔杼，曹人，邾人，杞人，次于鄫。<AlignEnd Key=\"920\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"921\" RefId=\"魯襄公元年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公元年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，楚公子壬夫帥師侵宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"921\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"922\" RefId=\"魯襄公元年九月\" Term=\"魯襄公元年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，辛酉，天王崩，邾子來朝。<AlignEnd Key=\"922\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"923\" RefId=\"魯襄公元年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公元年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，衛侯使公孫剽來聘，晉侯使荀罃來聘。<AlignEnd Key=\"923\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":890,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129949","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00152","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公二年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"924\" RefId=\"魯襄公二年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公二年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，葬簡王，鄭師伐宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"924\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"925\" RefId=\"魯襄公二年五月\" Term=\"魯襄公二年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月，庚寅，夫人姜氏薨。<AlignEnd Key=\"925\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"926\" RefId=\"魯襄公二年六月\" Term=\"魯襄公二年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，庚辰，鄭伯睔卒，晉師，宋師，衛甯殖，侵鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"926\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"927\" RefId=\"魯襄公二年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公二年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，仲孫蔑會晉荀罃，宋華元，衛孫林父，曹人，邾人，于戚，己丑，葬我小君齊姜，叔孫豹如宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"927\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"928\" RefId=\"魯襄公二年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公二年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，仲孫蔑會晉荀罃，齊崔杼，宋華元，衛孫林父，曹人，邾人，滕人，薛人，小邾人，于戚，遂城虎牢，楚殺其大夫公子申。<AlignEnd Key=\"928\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":891,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129950","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00153","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公三年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"929\" RefId=\"魯襄公三年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公三年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，楚公子嬰齊帥師伐吳，公如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"929\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"930\" RefId=\"魯襄公三年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公三年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，壬戌，公及晉侯盟于長樗，公至自晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"930\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"931\" RefId=\"魯襄公三年六月\" Term=\"魯襄公三年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，公會單子，晉侯，宋公，衛侯，鄭伯，莒子，邾子，齊世子光，己未，同盟于雞澤，陳侯使袁僑如會，戊寅，叔孫豹，及諸侯之大夫，及陳袁僑盟。<AlignEnd Key=\"931\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"932\" RefId=\"魯襄公三年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公三年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，公至自會。<AlignEnd Key=\"932\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"933\" RefId=\"魯襄公三年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公三年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，晉荀罃帥師伐許。<AlignEnd Key=\"933\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":892,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129951","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00154","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公四年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"934\" RefId=\"魯襄公四年三月\" Term=\"魯襄公四年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王三月，己酉，陳，侯午卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"934\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"935\" RefId=\"魯襄公四年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公四年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，叔孫豹如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"935\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"936\" RefId=\"魯襄公四年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公四年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，戊子，夫人姒氏薨，葬陳成公，八月，辛亥，葬我小君定姒。<AlignEnd Key=\"936\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"937\" RefId=\"魯襄公四年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公四年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，公如晉，陳人圍頓。<AlignEnd Key=\"937\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":893,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129952","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00155","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公五年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"938\" RefId=\"魯襄公五年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公五年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，公至自晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"938\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"939\" RefId=\"魯襄公五年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公五年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，鄭伯使公子發來聘，叔孫豹鄫，世子巫，如晉，仲孫蔑，衛孫林父，會吳于善道。<AlignEnd Key=\"939\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"940\" RefId=\"魯襄公五年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公五年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，大雩，楚殺其大夫公子壬夫，公會晉侯，宋公，陳侯，衛侯，鄭伯，曹伯，莒子，邾子，滕子，薛伯，齊世子光，吳人，鄫人，于戚，公至自會。<AlignEnd Key=\"940\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"941\" RefId=\"魯襄公五年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公五年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，戍陳楚公子貞帥師伐陳，公會晉侯，宋公，衛侯，鄭伯，曹伯，齊世子光，救陳。<AlignEnd Key=\"941\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"942\" RefId=\"魯襄公五年十二月\" Term=\"魯襄公五年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，公至自救陳，辛未，季孫行父卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"942\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":894,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129953","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00156","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公六年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"943\" RefId=\"魯襄公六年三月\" Term=\"魯襄公六年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王三月，壬午，杞伯姑容卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"943\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"944\" RefId=\"魯襄公六年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公六年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，宋華弱來奔。<AlignEnd Key=\"944\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"945\" RefId=\"魯襄公六年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公六年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，葬杞桓公，滕子來朝，莒人滅鄫。<AlignEnd Key=\"945\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"946\" RefId=\"魯襄公六年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公六年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，叔孫豹如邾，季孫宿如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"946\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"947\" RefId=\"魯襄公六年十二月\" Term=\"魯襄公六年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，齊侯滅萊。<AlignEnd Key=\"947\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":895,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129954","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00157","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公七年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"948\" RefId=\"魯襄公七年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公七年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，郯子來朝。<AlignEnd Key=\"948\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"949\" RefId=\"魯襄公七年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公七年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，三卜郊不從，乃免牲，小邾子來朝，城費。<AlignEnd Key=\"949\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"950\" RefId=\"魯襄公七年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公七年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，季孫宿如衛。<AlignEnd Key=\"950\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"951\" RefId=\"魯襄公七年八月\" Term=\"魯襄公七年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>八月，螽。<AlignEnd Key=\"951\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"952\" RefId=\"魯襄公七年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公七年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，衛侯使孫林父來聘，壬戌，及孫林父盟，楚公子貞帥師圍陳。<AlignEnd Key=\"952\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"953\" RefId=\"魯襄公七年十二月\" Term=\"魯襄公七年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，公會晉侯，宋公，陳侯，衛侯，曹伯，莒子，邾子，于鄬，鄭伯髡頑如會，未見諸侯，丙戌，卒于鄵，陳侯逃歸。<AlignEnd Key=\"953\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":896,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129955","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00158","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公八年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"954\" RefId=\"魯襄公八年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公八年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"954\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"955\" RefId=\"魯襄公八年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公八年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，葬鄭僖公，鄭人侵蔡，獲蔡公子燮，季孫宿會晉侯，鄭伯，齊人，宋人，衛人，邾人，于邢丘，公至自晉，莒人伐我東鄙。<AlignEnd Key=\"955\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"956\" RefId=\"魯襄公八年九月\" Term=\"魯襄公八年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，九月，大雩。<AlignEnd Key=\"956\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"957\" RefId=\"魯襄公八年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，楚公子貞帥師伐鄭，晉侯使士\u5304來聘。<AlignEnd Key=\"957\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":897,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129956","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00159","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公九年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"958\" RefId=\"魯襄公九年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公九年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，宋災。<AlignEnd Key=\"958\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"959\" RefId=\"魯襄公九年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公九年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，季孫宿如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"959\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"960\" RefId=\"魯襄公九年五月\" Term=\"魯襄公九年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>五月，辛酉，夫人姜氏薨。<AlignEnd Key=\"960\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"961\" RefId=\"魯襄公九年八月\" Term=\"魯襄公九年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月，癸未，葬我小君穆姜。<AlignEnd Key=\"961\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"962\" RefId=\"魯襄公九年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公九年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，公會晉侯，宋公，衛侯，曹伯，莒子，邾子，滕子，薛伯，杞伯，小邾子，齊世子光，伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"962\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"963\" RefId=\"魯襄公九年十二月\" Term=\"魯襄公九年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，己亥，同盟于戲，楚子伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"963\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":898,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129957","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00160","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公十年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"964\" RefId=\"魯襄公十年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公十年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，公會晉侯，宋公，衛侯，曹伯，莒子，邾子，滕子，薛伯，杞伯，小邾子，齊世子光，會吳于柤。<AlignEnd Key=\"964\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"965\" RefId=\"魯襄公十年五月\" Term=\"魯襄公十年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月，甲午，遂滅偪陽，公至自會，楚公子貞，鄭公孫輒，帥師伐宋，晉師伐秦。<AlignEnd Key=\"965\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"966\" RefId=\"魯襄公十年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公十年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，莒人伐我東鄙，公會晉侯，宋公，衛侯，曹伯，莒子，邾子，齊世子光，滕子，薛伯，杞，伯，小邾子，伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"966\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"967\" RefId=\"魯襄公十年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公十年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，盜殺鄭公子騑，公子發，公孫輒，戍鄭虎牢，楚公子貞帥師救鄭，公至自伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"967\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":899,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129958","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00161","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公十一年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"968\" RefId=\"魯襄公十一年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公十一年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，作三軍。<AlignEnd Key=\"968\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"969\" RefId=\"魯襄公十一年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公十一年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，四卜郊不從，乃不郊，鄭公孫舍之帥師侵宋，公會晉侯，宋公，衛侯，曹伯，齊世子光，莒子，邾子，滕子，薛伯，杞伯，小邾子，伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"969\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"970\" RefId=\"魯襄公十一年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公十一年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，己未，同盟于亳城北，公至自伐鄭，楚子，鄭伯，伐宋，公會晉侯，宋公，衛侯，曹伯，齊世子光，莒子，邾子，滕子，薛伯，杞伯，小邾子，伐鄭，會于蕭魚，公至自會，楚執鄭行人，良霄。<AlignEnd Key=\"970\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"971\" RefId=\"魯襄公十一年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公十一年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，秦人伐晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"971\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":900,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129959","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00162","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公十二年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"972\" RefId=\"魯襄公十二年二月\" Term=\"魯襄公十二年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王二月，莒人伐我東鄙，圖台，季孫宿帥師救台，遂入鄆。<AlignEnd Key=\"972\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"973\" RefId=\"魯襄公十二年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公十二年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，晉侯使士魴來聘。<AlignEnd Key=\"973\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"974\" RefId=\"魯襄公十二年九月\" Term=\"魯襄公十二年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，九月，吳子乘卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"974\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"975\" RefId=\"魯襄公十二年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公十二年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，楚公子貞帥師侵宋，公如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"975\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":901,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129960","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00163","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公十三年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"976\" RefId=\"魯襄公十三年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公十三年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，公至自晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"976\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"977\" RefId=\"魯襄公十三年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公十三年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，取邿。<AlignEnd Key=\"977\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"978\" RefId=\"魯襄公十三年九月\" Term=\"魯襄公十三年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，九月，庚辰，楚子審卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"978\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"979\" RefId=\"魯襄公十三年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公十三年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，城防。<AlignEnd Key=\"979\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":902,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129961","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00164","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公十四年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"980\" RefId=\"魯襄公十四年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公十四年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，季孫宿叔老會晉士\u5304，齊人，宋人，衛人，鄭公孫蠆，曹人，莒人，邾人，滕人，薛人，杞人，小邾人，會吳于向。<AlignEnd Key=\"980\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"981\" RefId=\"魯襄公十四年二月\" Term=\"魯襄公十四年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>二月，乙未朔，日有食之。<AlignEnd Key=\"981\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"982\" RefId=\"魯襄公十四年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公十四年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，叔孫豹會晉荀偃，齊人，宋人，衛北宮括，鄭公孫蠆，曹人，莒人，邾人，滕人，薛人，杞人，小邾人，伐秦，己未，衛侯出奔齊，莒人侵我東鄙。<AlignEnd Key=\"982\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"983\" RefId=\"魯襄公十四年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公十四年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，楚公子貞帥師伐吳。<AlignEnd Key=\"983\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"984\" RefId=\"魯襄公十四年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公十四年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，季孫宿會晉士\u5304，宋華閱，衛孫林父，鄭公孫蠆，莒人，邾人，于戚。<AlignEnd Key=\"984\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":903,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129962","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00165","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公十五年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"985\" RefId=\"魯襄公十五年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公十五年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，宋公使同戌來聘。<AlignEnd Key=\"985\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"986\" RefId=\"魯襄公十五年二月\" Term=\"魯襄公十五年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>二月，己亥，及向戌盟于劉，劉夏逆王后于齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"986\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"987\" RefId=\"魯襄公十五年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公十五年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，齊侯伐我北鄙，圍成，公救成，至遇，季孫宿，叔孫豹，帥師城成郛。<AlignEnd Key=\"987\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"988\" RefId=\"魯襄公十五年八月\" Term=\"魯襄公十五年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月，丁巳，日有食之，邾人伐我南鄙。<AlignEnd Key=\"988\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"989\" RefId=\"魯襄公十五年十一月\" Term=\"魯襄公十五年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有一月，癸亥，晉侯周卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"989\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":904,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129963","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00166","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公十六年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"990\" RefId=\"魯襄公十六年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公十六年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，葬晉悼公。<AlignEnd Key=\"990\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"991\" RefId=\"魯襄公十六年三月\" Term=\"魯襄公十六年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，公會晉侯，宋公，衛侯，鄭伯，曹伯，莒子，邾子，薛伯，杞伯，小邾子，于溴梁，戊寅，大夫盟，晉人執莒子，邾子，以歸，齊侯伐我北鄙。<AlignEnd Key=\"991\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"992\" RefId=\"魯襄公十六年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公十六年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，公至自會。<AlignEnd Key=\"992\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"993\" RefId=\"魯襄公十六年五月\" Term=\"魯襄公十六年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>五月，甲子，地震，叔老會鄭伯，晉荀偃，衛甯殖，宋人，伐許。<AlignEnd Key=\"993\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"994\" RefId=\"魯襄公十六年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公十六年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，齊侯伐我北鄙，圍郕，大雩。<AlignEnd Key=\"994\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"995\" RefId=\"魯襄公十六年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公十六年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，叔孫豹如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"995\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":905,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129964","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00167","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公十七年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"996\" RefId=\"魯襄公十七年二月\" Term=\"魯襄公十七年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王二月，庚午，邾子牼卒，宋人伐陳。<AlignEnd Key=\"996\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"997\" RefId=\"魯襄公十七年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公十七年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，衛石買帥師伐曹。<AlignEnd Key=\"997\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"998\" RefId=\"魯襄公十七年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公十七年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，齊侯伐我北鄙，圍桃，高厚帥師伐我北鄙，圍防。<AlignEnd Key=\"998\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"999\" RefId=\"魯襄公十七年九月\" Term=\"魯襄公十七年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，大雩，宋華臣出奔陳。<AlignEnd Key=\"999\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1000\" RefId=\"魯襄公十七年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公十七年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，邾人伐我南鄙。<AlignEnd Key=\"1000\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":906,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129965","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00168","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公十八年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1001\" RefId=\"魯襄公十八年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公十八年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，白狄來。<AlignEnd Key=\"1001\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1002\" RefId=\"魯襄公十八年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公十八年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，晉人執衛行人石買。<AlignEnd Key=\"1002\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1003\" RefId=\"魯襄公十八年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公十八年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，齊師伐我北鄙。<AlignEnd Key=\"1003\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1004\" RefId=\"魯襄公十八年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公十八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，公會晉侯，宋公，衛侯，鄭伯，曹伯，莒子，邾子，滕子，薛伯，杞伯，小邾子，同圍齊，曹伯負芻卒于師，楚公子午帥師伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"1004\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":907,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129966","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00169","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公十九年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1005\" RefId=\"魯襄公十九年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公十九年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，諸侯盟于祝柯，晉人執邾子，公至自伐齊，取邾田自漷水，季孫宿如晉，葬曹成公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1005\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1006\" RefId=\"魯襄公十九年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公十九年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，衛孫林父帥師伐齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"1006\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1007\" RefId=\"魯襄公十九年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公十九年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，辛卯，齊侯環卒，晉士\u5304帥師侵齊，至穀，聞齊侯卒，乃還。<AlignEnd Key=\"1007\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1008\" RefId=\"魯襄公十九年八月\" Term=\"魯襄公十九年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>八月，丙辰，仲孫蔑卒，齊殺其大夫高厚，鄭殺其大夫公子嘉。<AlignEnd Key=\"1008\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1009\" RefId=\"魯襄公十九年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公十九年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，葬齊靈公，城西郛，叔孫豹會晉士\u5304于柯，城武城。<AlignEnd Key=\"1009\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":908,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129967","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00170","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公二十年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1010\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，辛亥，仲孫速會莒人盟于向。<AlignEnd Key=\"1010\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1011\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十年六月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，六月，庚申，公會晉侯，齊侯，宋公，衛侯，鄭伯，曹伯，莒子，邾子，滕子，薛伯，杞伯，小邾子，盟于澶淵。<AlignEnd Key=\"1011\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1012\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，公至自會，仲孫速帥師伐邾，蔡殺其大夫公子燮，蔡公子履出奔楚，陳侯之弟黃出奔楚，叔老如齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"1012\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1013\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，丙辰朔，日有食之，季孫宿如宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"1013\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":909,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129968","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00171","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公二十一年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1014\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十一年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十一年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公如晉，邾庶其以漆閭丘來奔。<AlignEnd Key=\"1014\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1015\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十一年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十一年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，公至自晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"1015\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1016\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十一年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十一年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，晉欒盈出奔楚。<AlignEnd Key=\"1016\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1017\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十一年九月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十一年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，庚戌朔，日有食之。<AlignEnd Key=\"1017\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1018\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十一年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十一年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，庚辰朔，日有食之，曹伯來朝，公會晉侯，齊侯，宋公，衛侯，鄭伯，曹伯，莒子，邾子，于商任。<AlignEnd Key=\"1018\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":910,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129969","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00172","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公二十二年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1019\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十二年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十二年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公至自會。<AlignEnd Key=\"1019\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1020\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十二年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十二年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月。<AlignEnd Key=\"1020\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1021\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十二年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十二年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，辛酉，叔老卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1021\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1022\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十二年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十二年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，公會晉侯，齊侯，宋公，衛侯，鄭伯，曹伯，莒子，邾子，薛伯，杞伯，小邾子，于沙隨，公至自會，楚殺其大夫公子追舒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1022\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":911,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129970","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00173","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公二十三年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1023\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十三年二月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十三年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王二月，癸酉朔，日有食之。<AlignEnd Key=\"1023\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1024\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十三年三月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十三年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，己巳，杞伯\u5304卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1024\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1025\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十三年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十三年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，邾畀我來奔，葬杞孝公，陳殺其大夫慶虎及慶寅，陳侯之弟黃，自楚歸于陳，晉欒盈復入于晉，入于曲沃。<AlignEnd Key=\"1025\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1026\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十三年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十三年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，齊侯伐衛，遂伐晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"1026\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1027\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十三年八月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十三年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>八月，叔孫豹帥師救晉，次于雍榆，己卯，仲孫速卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1027\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1028\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十三年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十三年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，乙亥，臧孫紇出奔邾，晉人殺欒盈，齊侯襲莒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1028\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":912,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129971","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00174","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公二十四年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1029\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十四年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十四年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，叔孫豹如晉，仲孫羯帥師侵齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"1029\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1030\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十四年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十四年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，楚子伐吳。<AlignEnd Key=\"1030\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1031\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十四年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十四年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，甲子，朔，日有食之，既，齊崔杼帥師伐莒，大水。<AlignEnd Key=\"1031\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1032\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十四年八月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十四年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>八月，癸巳朔，日有食之，公會晉侯，宋公，衛侯，鄭伯，曹伯，莒子，邾子，滕子，薛伯，杞伯，小邾子，于夷儀。<AlignEnd Key=\"1032\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1033\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十四年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十四年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，楚子，蔡侯，陳侯，許男，伐鄭，公至自會，陳鍼宜咎出奔楚，叔孫豹如京師，大饑。<AlignEnd Key=\"1033\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":913,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129972","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00175","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公二十五年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1034\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十五年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十五年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，齊崔杼帥師伐我北鄙。<AlignEnd Key=\"1034\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1035\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十五年五月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十五年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月，乙亥，齊崔杼弒其君光，公會晉侯，宋公，衛侯，鄭伯，曹伯，莒子，邾子，滕子，薛伯，杞伯，小邾子，于夷儀。<AlignEnd Key=\"1035\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1036\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十五年六月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十五年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，壬子，鄭公孫舍之帥師入陳。<AlignEnd Key=\"1036\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1037\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十五年八月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十五年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月，己巳，諸侯同盟于重丘，公至自會，衛侯入于夷儀，楚屈建帥師滅舒鳩。<AlignEnd Key=\"1037\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1038\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十五年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十五年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，鄭公孫夏帥師伐陳。<AlignEnd Key=\"1038\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1039\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十五年十二月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十五年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，吳子遏伐楚，門于巢，卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1039\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":914,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129973","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00176","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公二十六年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1040\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十六年二月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十六年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王二月，辛卯，衛甯喜弒其君剽，衛孫林父入于戚以叛，甲午，衛侯衎復歸于衛。<AlignEnd Key=\"1040\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1041\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十六年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十六年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，晉侯使荀吳來聘，公會晉人，鄭良霄，宋人，曹人，于澶淵。<AlignEnd Key=\"1041\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1042\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十六年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十六年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，宋公殺其世子痤，晉人執衛甯喜。<AlignEnd Key=\"1042\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1043\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十六年八月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十六年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>八月，壬午，許男甯卒于楚。<AlignEnd Key=\"1043\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1044\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十六年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十六年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，楚子，蔡侯，陳侯，伐鄭，葬許靈公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1044\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":915,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129974","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00177","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公二十七年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1045\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十七年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十七年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，齊侯使慶封來聘。<AlignEnd Key=\"1045\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1046\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十七年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十七年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，叔孫豹會晉趙武，楚屈建，蔡公孫歸生，衛石惡，陳孔奐，鄭良霄，許人，曹人，于宋，衛殺其大夫甯喜，衛侯之弟鱄出奔晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"1046\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1047\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十七年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十七年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，辛巳，豹及諸侯之大夫盟于宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"1047\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1048\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十七年十二月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十七年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有二月，乙卯，朔，日有食之。<AlignEnd Key=\"1048\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":916,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129975","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00178","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公二十八年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1049\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十八年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十八年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，無冰。<AlignEnd Key=\"1049\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1050\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十八年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十八年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，衛石惡出奔晉，邾子來朝。<AlignEnd Key=\"1050\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1051\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十八年八月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十八年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月，大雩，仲孫羯如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"1051\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1052\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十八年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，齊慶封來奔。<AlignEnd Key=\"1052\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1053\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十八年十一月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十八年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有一月，公如楚。<AlignEnd Key=\"1053\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1054\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十八年十二月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十八年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月甲寅，天王崩，乙未，楚子昭卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1054\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":917,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129976","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00179","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公二十九年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1055\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十九年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十九年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公在楚。<AlignEnd Key=\"1055\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1056\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十九年五月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十九年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月，公至自楚，庚午，衛侯衎卒，閽弒吳子餘祭，仲孫羯會晉荀盈，齊高止，宋華定，衛世叔儀，鄭公孫段，曹人，莒人，滕人，薛人，小邾人，城杞，晉侯使士鞅來聘，杞子來盟，吳子使札來聘。<AlignEnd Key=\"1056\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1057\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十九年九月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十九年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，九月，葬衛獻公，齊高止出奔北燕。<AlignEnd Key=\"1057\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1058\" RefId=\"魯襄公二十九年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公二十九年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，仲孫羯如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"1058\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":918,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129977","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00180","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公三十年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1059\" RefId=\"魯襄公三十年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公三十年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，楚子使薳罷來聘。<AlignEnd Key=\"1059\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1060\" RefId=\"魯襄公三十年四月\" Term=\"魯襄公三十年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，蔡世子般弒其君固。<AlignEnd Key=\"1060\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1061\" RefId=\"魯襄公三十年五月\" Term=\"魯襄公三十年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>五月，甲午，宋災，宋伯姬卒，天王殺其弟佞夫，王子瑕奔晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"1061\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1062\" RefId=\"魯襄公三十年七月\" Term=\"魯襄公三十年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，叔弓如宋，葬宋共姬，鄭良霄出奔許，自許入于鄭，鄭人殺良霄。<AlignEnd Key=\"1062\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1063\" RefId=\"魯襄公三十年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公三十年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，葬蔡景公，晉人，齊人，宋人，衛人，鄭人，曹人，莒人，邾人，滕人，薛人，杞人，小邾人，會于澶淵，宋災故。<AlignEnd Key=\"1063\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":919,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129978","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00181","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯襄公三十一年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1064\" RefId=\"魯襄公三十一年正月\" Term=\"魯襄公三十一年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月。<AlignEnd Key=\"1064\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1065\" RefId=\"魯襄公三十一年六月\" Term=\"魯襄公三十一年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，六月，辛巳，公薨于楚宮。<AlignEnd Key=\"1065\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1066\" RefId=\"魯襄公三十一年九月\" Term=\"魯襄公三十一年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，九月，癸巳，子野卒，己亥，仲孫羯卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1066\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1067\" RefId=\"魯襄公三十一年十月\" Term=\"魯襄公三十一年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，滕子來會葬，癸酉，葬我君襄公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1067\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1068\" RefId=\"魯襄公三十一年十一月\" Term=\"魯襄公三十一年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有一月，莒人弒其君密州。<AlignEnd Key=\"1068\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":920,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129979","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00182","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公元年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1069\" RefId=\"魯昭公元年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公元年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公即位，叔孫豹會晉趙武，楚公子圍，齊國弱，宋向戌，衛齊惡，陳公子招，蔡公孫歸生，鄭罕虎，許人，曹人，于虢。<AlignEnd Key=\"1069\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1070\" RefId=\"魯昭公元年三月\" Term=\"魯昭公元年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月\u2027取鄆。<AlignEnd Key=\"1070\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1071\" RefId=\"魯昭公元年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公元年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，秦伯之弟鍼出奔晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"1071\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1072\" RefId=\"魯昭公元年六月\" Term=\"魯昭公元年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月丁巳，邾子華卒，晉荀吳帥師敗狄于大鹵。<AlignEnd Key=\"1072\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1073\" RefId=\"魯昭公元年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公元年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，莒去疾自齊入于莒，莒展輿出奔吳，叔弓帥師疆鄆田，葬邾悼公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1073\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1074\" RefId=\"魯昭公元年十一月\" Term=\"魯昭公元年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有一月，己酉，楚子麇卒，公子比出奔晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"1074\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":921,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129980","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00183","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公二年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1075\" RefId=\"魯昭公二年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公二年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，晉侯使韓起來聘。<AlignEnd Key=\"1075\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1076\" RefId=\"魯昭公二年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公二年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，叔弓如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"1076\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1077\" RefId=\"魯昭公二年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公二年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，鄭殺其大夫公孫黑。<AlignEnd Key=\"1077\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1078\" RefId=\"魯昭公二年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公二年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，公如晉，至河乃復，季孫宿如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"1078\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":922,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129981","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00184","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公三年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1079\" RefId=\"魯昭公三年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公三年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，丁未，滕子原卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1079\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1080\" RefId=\"魯昭公三年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公三年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，叔弓如滕。<AlignEnd Key=\"1080\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1081\" RefId=\"魯昭公三年五月\" Term=\"魯昭公三年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>五月，葬滕成公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1081\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1082\" RefId=\"魯昭公三年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公三年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，小邾子來朝。<AlignEnd Key=\"1082\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1083\" RefId=\"魯昭公三年八月\" Term=\"魯昭公三年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>八月，大雩。<AlignEnd Key=\"1083\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1084\" RefId=\"魯昭公三年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公三年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，大雨雹，北燕伯款出奔齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"1084\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":923,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129982","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00185","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公四年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1085\" RefId=\"魯昭公四年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公四年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，大雨雹。<AlignEnd Key=\"1085\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1086\" RefId=\"魯昭公四年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公四年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，楚子，蔡侯，陳侯，鄭伯，許男，徐子，滕子，頓子，胡子，沈子，小邾子，宋世子，佐淮夷會于申，楚人執徐子。<AlignEnd Key=\"1086\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1087\" RefId=\"魯昭公四年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公四年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，楚子，蔡侯，陳侯，許男，頓子，胡子，沈子，淮夷，伐吳，執齊慶封，殺之，遂滅賴。<AlignEnd Key=\"1087\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1088\" RefId=\"魯昭公四年九月\" Term=\"魯昭公四年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，取鄫。<AlignEnd Key=\"1088\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1089\" RefId=\"魯昭公四年十二月\" Term=\"魯昭公四年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有二月，乙卯，叔孫豹卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1089\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":924,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129983","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00186","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公五年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1090\" RefId=\"魯昭公五年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公五年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，舍中軍，楚殺其大夫屈申，公如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"1090\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1091\" RefId=\"魯昭公五年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公五年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，莒牟夷以牟婁及防茲來奔。<AlignEnd Key=\"1091\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1092\" RefId=\"魯昭公五年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公五年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，公至自晉，戊辰，叔弓帥師敗莒師于蚡泉，秦伯卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1092\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1093\" RefId=\"魯昭公五年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公五年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，楚子，蔡侯，陳侯，許男，頓子，沈子，徐人，越人，伐吳。<AlignEnd Key=\"1093\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":925,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129984","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00187","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公六年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1094\" RefId=\"魯昭公六年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公六年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，杞柏益姑卒，葬秦景公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1094\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1095\" RefId=\"魯昭公六年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公六年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，季孫宿如晉，葬杞文公，宋華合比，出奔衛。<AlignEnd Key=\"1095\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1096\" RefId=\"魯昭公六年九月\" Term=\"魯昭公六年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，九月，大雩，楚薳罷帥師伐吳。<AlignEnd Key=\"1096\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1097\" RefId=\"魯昭公六年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公六年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，叔弓如楚，齊侯伐北燕。<AlignEnd Key=\"1097\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":926,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129985","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00188","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公七年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1098\" RefId=\"魯昭公七年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公七年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，暨齊平。<AlignEnd Key=\"1098\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1099\" RefId=\"魯昭公七年三月\" Term=\"魯昭公七年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，公如楚，叔孫婼如齊蒞盟。<AlignEnd Key=\"1099\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1100\" RefId=\"魯昭公七年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公七年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，甲辰，朔，日有食之。<AlignEnd Key=\"1100\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1101\" RefId=\"魯昭公七年八月\" Term=\"魯昭公七年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月，戊辰，衛侯惡卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1101\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1102\" RefId=\"魯昭公七年九月\" Term=\"魯昭公七年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，公至自楚。<AlignEnd Key=\"1102\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1103\" RefId=\"魯昭公七年十一月\" Term=\"魯昭公七年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有一月，癸未，季孫宿卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1103\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1104\" RefId=\"魯昭公七年十二月\" Term=\"魯昭公七年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，癸亥，葬衛襄公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1104\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":927,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129986","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00189","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公八年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1105\" RefId=\"魯昭公八年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公八年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，陳侯之弟招，殺陳世子偃師。<AlignEnd Key=\"1105\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1106\" RefId=\"魯昭公八年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公八年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，辛丑，陳侯溺卒，叔弓如晉，楚人執陳行人干徵師，殺之，陳公子留，出奔鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"1106\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1107\" RefId=\"魯昭公八年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公八年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，蒐于紅，陳人殺其大夫公子過，大雩。<AlignEnd Key=\"1107\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1108\" RefId=\"魯昭公八年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，壬午，楚師滅陳，執陳公子招，放之于越，殺陳孔奐，葬陳哀公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1108\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":928,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129987","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00190","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公九年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1109\" RefId=\"魯昭公九年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公九年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，叔弓會楚子于陳，許遷于夷。<AlignEnd Key=\"1109\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1110\" RefId=\"魯昭公九年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公九年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，陳災。<AlignEnd Key=\"1110\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1111\" RefId=\"魯昭公九年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公九年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，仲孫貜如齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"1111\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1112\" RefId=\"魯昭公九年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公九年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，築郎囿。<AlignEnd Key=\"1112\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":929,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129988","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00191","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公十年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1113\" RefId=\"魯昭公十年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公十年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月。<AlignEnd Key=\"1113\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1114\" RefId=\"魯昭公十年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公十年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，齊欒施來奔。<AlignEnd Key=\"1114\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1115\" RefId=\"魯昭公十年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公十年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，季孫意如叔弓，仲孫貜帥師伐莒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1115\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1116\" RefId=\"魯昭公十年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公十年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>戊子，晉侯彪卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1116\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1117\" RefId=\"魯昭公十年九月\" Term=\"魯昭公十年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，叔孫婼如晉，葬晉平公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1117\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1118\" RefId=\"魯昭公十年十二月\" Term=\"魯昭公十年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，甲子，宋公成卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1118\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":930,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129989","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00192","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公十一年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1119\" RefId=\"魯昭公十一年二月\" Term=\"魯昭公十一年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王二月，叔弓如宋，葬宋平公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1119\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1120\" RefId=\"魯昭公十一年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公十一年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，丁巳，楚子虔誘蔡侯般，殺之于申，楚公子杞疾帥師圍蔡。<AlignEnd Key=\"1120\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1121\" RefId=\"魯昭公十一年五月\" Term=\"魯昭公十一年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>五月，甲申，夫人歸氏薨，大蒐于比蒲，仲孫貜會邾子盟于祲祥。<AlignEnd Key=\"1121\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1122\" RefId=\"魯昭公十一年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公十一年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，季孫意如會，晉韓起，齊國弱，宋華亥，衛北宮佗，鄭罕虎，曹人，杞人，于厥憖。<AlignEnd Key=\"1122\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1123\" RefId=\"魯昭公十一年九月\" Term=\"魯昭公十一年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，己亥，葬我小君齊歸。<AlignEnd Key=\"1123\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1124\" RefId=\"魯昭公十一年十一月\" Term=\"魯昭公十一年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有一月，丁酉，楚師滅蔡，執蔡世子有以歸用之。<AlignEnd Key=\"1124\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":931,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129990","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00193","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公十二年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1125\" RefId=\"魯昭公十二年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公十二年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，齊高偃帥師納北燕伯于陽。<AlignEnd Key=\"1125\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1126\" RefId=\"魯昭公十二年三月\" Term=\"魯昭公十二年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，壬申，鄭伯嘉卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1126\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1127\" RefId=\"魯昭公十二年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公十二年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，宋公使華定來聘，公如晉至河乃復。<AlignEnd Key=\"1127\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1128\" RefId=\"魯昭公十二年五月\" Term=\"魯昭公十二年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>五月，葬鄭簡公，楚殺其大夫成熊。<AlignEnd Key=\"1128\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1129\" RefId=\"魯昭公十二年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公十二年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月。<AlignEnd Key=\"1129\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1130\" RefId=\"魯昭公十二年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公十二年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，公子憖出奔齊，楚子伐徐，晉伐鮮虞。<AlignEnd Key=\"1130\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":932,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129991","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00194","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公十三年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1131\" RefId=\"魯昭公十三年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公十三年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，叔弓帥師圍費。<AlignEnd Key=\"1131\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1132\" RefId=\"魯昭公十三年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公十三年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，楚公子比自晉歸于楚，弒其君虔于乾谿，楚公子棄疾殺公子比。<AlignEnd Key=\"1132\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1133\" RefId=\"魯昭公十三年八月\" Term=\"魯昭公十三年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，公會劉子，晉侯，齊侯，宋公，衛侯，鄭伯，曹伯，莒子，邾子，滕子，薛伯，杞伯，小邾子，于平丘，八月，甲戌，同盟于平丘，公不與盟，晉人執季孫意如以歸，公至自會，蔡侯廬歸于蔡，陳侯吳歸于陳。<AlignEnd Key=\"1133\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1134\" RefId=\"魯昭公十三年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公十三年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，葬蔡靈公，公如晉，至河乃復，吳滅州來。<AlignEnd Key=\"1134\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":933,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129992","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00195","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公十四年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1135\" RefId=\"魯昭公十四年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公十四年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，意如至自晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"1135\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1136\" RefId=\"魯昭公十四年三月\" Term=\"魯昭公十四年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，曹伯滕卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1136\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1137\" RefId=\"魯昭公十四年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公十四年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月。<AlignEnd Key=\"1137\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1138\" RefId=\"魯昭公十四年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公十四年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，葬曹武公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1138\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1139\" RefId=\"魯昭公十四年八月\" Term=\"魯昭公十四年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>八月，莒子去疾卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1139\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1140\" RefId=\"魯昭公十四年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公十四年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，莒殺其公子意恢。<AlignEnd Key=\"1140\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":934,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129993","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00196","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公十五年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1141\" RefId=\"魯昭公十五年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公十五年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，吳子夷末卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1141\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1142\" RefId=\"魯昭公十五年二月\" Term=\"魯昭公十五年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>二月，癸酉，有事于武宮籥入叔弓卒，去樂卒事。<AlignEnd Key=\"1142\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1143\" RefId=\"魯昭公十五年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公十五年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，蔡朝吳出奔鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"1143\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1144\" RefId=\"魯昭公十五年六月\" Term=\"魯昭公十五年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，丁巳，朔日有食之。<AlignEnd Key=\"1144\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1145\" RefId=\"魯昭公十五年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公十五年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，晉荀吳帥師伐鮮虞。<AlignEnd Key=\"1145\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1146\" RefId=\"魯昭公十五年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公十五年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，公如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"1146\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":935,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129994","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00197","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公十六年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1147\" RefId=\"魯昭公十六年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公十六年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，齊侯伐徐，楚子誘戎蠻子殺之。<AlignEnd Key=\"1147\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1148\" RefId=\"魯昭公十六年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公十六年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，公至自晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"1148\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1149\" RefId=\"魯昭公十六年八月\" Term=\"魯昭公十六年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月，己亥，晉侯夷卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1149\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1150\" RefId=\"魯昭公十六年九月\" Term=\"魯昭公十六年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，大雩，季孫意如如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"1150\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1151\" RefId=\"魯昭公十六年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公十六年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，葬晉昭公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1151\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":936,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129995","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00198","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公十七年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1152\" RefId=\"魯昭公十七年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公十七年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，小邾子來朝。<AlignEnd Key=\"1152\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1153\" RefId=\"魯昭公十七年六月\" Term=\"魯昭公十七年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，六月，甲戌，朔，日有食之。<AlignEnd Key=\"1153\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1154\" RefId=\"魯昭公十七年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公十七年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，郯子來朝。<AlignEnd Key=\"1154\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1155\" RefId=\"魯昭公十七年八月\" Term=\"魯昭公十七年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>八月，晉荀吳帥師滅陸渾之戎。<AlignEnd Key=\"1155\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1156\" RefId=\"魯昭公十七年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公十七年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，有星孛于大辰，楚人及吳戰于長岸。<AlignEnd Key=\"1156\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":937,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129996","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00199","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公十八年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1157\" RefId=\"魯昭公十八年三月\" Term=\"魯昭公十八年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王三月，曹伯須卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1157\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1158\" RefId=\"魯昭公十八年五月\" Term=\"魯昭公十八年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月，壬午，宋，衛，陳，鄭，災。<AlignEnd Key=\"1158\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1159\" RefId=\"魯昭公十八年六月\" Term=\"魯昭公十八年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，邾人入鄅。<AlignEnd Key=\"1159\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1160\" RefId=\"魯昭公十八年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公十八年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，葬曹平公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1160\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1161\" RefId=\"魯昭公十八年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公十八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，許遷于白羽。<AlignEnd Key=\"1161\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":938,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129997","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00200","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公十九年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1162\" RefId=\"魯昭公十九年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公十九年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，宋公伐邾。<AlignEnd Key=\"1162\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1163\" RefId=\"魯昭公十九年五月\" Term=\"魯昭公十九年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月，戊辰，許世子止弒其君買，己卯，地震。<AlignEnd Key=\"1163\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1164\" RefId=\"魯昭公十九年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公十九年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋\u2027齊高發帥師伐莒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1164\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1165\" RefId=\"魯昭公十九年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公十九年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，葬許悼公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1165\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":939,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129998","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00201","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公二十年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1166\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月。<AlignEnd Key=\"1166\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1167\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，曹公孫會自鄸出奔宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"1167\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1168\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，盜殺衛侯之兄縶。<AlignEnd Key=\"1168\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1169\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，宋華亥向寧，華定，出奔陳。<AlignEnd Key=\"1169\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1170\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十年十一月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有一月，辛卯，蔡侯盧卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1170\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":940,"docInfo":{"docId":"11129999","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00202","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公二十一年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1171\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十一年三月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十一年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王三月，葬蔡平公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1171\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1172\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十一年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十一年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，晉侯使士鞅來聘，宋華亥，向寧，華定，自陳入于宋南里以叛。<AlignEnd Key=\"1172\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1173\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十一年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十一年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，壬午，朔，日有食之。<AlignEnd Key=\"1173\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1174\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十一年八月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十一年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>八月，乙亥，叔輒卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1174\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1175\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十一年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十一年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，蔡侯朱出奔楚，公如晉至河乃復。<AlignEnd Key=\"1175\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":941,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130000","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00203","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公二十二年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1176\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十二年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十二年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，齊侯伐莒，宋，華亥，向寧，華定，自宋南里出奔楚，大蒐于昌間。<AlignEnd Key=\"1176\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1177\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十二年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十二年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，乙丑，天王崩，六月，叔鞅如京師葬景王，王室亂，劉子，單子，以王猛居于皇。<AlignEnd Key=\"1177\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1178\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十二年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十二年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，劉子，單子，以王猛入于王城。<AlignEnd Key=\"1178\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1179\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十二年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十二年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，王子猛卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1179\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1180\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十二年十二月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十二年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，癸酉，朔，日有食之。<AlignEnd Key=\"1180\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":942,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130001","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00204","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公二十三年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1181\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十三年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十三年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，叔孫婼如晉，癸丑，叔鞅卒，晉人執我行人叔孫婼，晉人圍郊。<AlignEnd Key=\"1181\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1182\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十三年六月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十三年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，六月，蔡侯東國卒于楚。<AlignEnd Key=\"1182\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1183\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十三年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十三年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，莒子庚輿來奔，戊辰，吳敗頓胡，沈，蔡，陳，許，之師于雞父，胡子髡，沈子逞，滅獲陳夏齧，天王居于狄，泉尹氏立王子朝。<AlignEnd Key=\"1183\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1184\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十三年八月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十三年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>八月，乙未，地震。<AlignEnd Key=\"1184\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1185\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十三年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十三年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，公如晉，至河，有疾，乃復。<AlignEnd Key=\"1185\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":943,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130002","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00205","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公二十四年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1186\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十四年三月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十四年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王三月，丙戌，仲孫貜卒，婼至自晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"1186\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1187\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十四年五月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十四年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月，乙未，朔，日有食之。<AlignEnd Key=\"1187\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1188\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十四年八月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十四年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月，大雩，丁酉，杞伯郁釐卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1188\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1189\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十四年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十四年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，吳滅巢，葬杞平公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1189\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":944,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130003","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00206","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公二十五年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1190\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十五年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十五年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，叔孫婼如宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"1190\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1191\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十五年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十五年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，叔詣會晉趙鞅，宋樂大心，衛北宮喜，鄭游吉，曹人，邾人，滕人，薛人，小邾人，于黃父，有鴝鵒來巢。<AlignEnd Key=\"1191\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1192\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十五年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十五年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，上辛，大雩，季辛，又雩。<AlignEnd Key=\"1192\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1193\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十五年九月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十五年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，巳月己亥，公孫于齊，次于陽州，齊侯唁公于野井。<AlignEnd Key=\"1193\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1194\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十五年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十五年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，戊辰，叔孫婼卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1194\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1195\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十五年十一月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十五年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有一月，己亥，宋公佐卒于曲棘。<AlignEnd Key=\"1195\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1196\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十五年十二月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十五年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，齊侯取鄆。<AlignEnd Key=\"1196\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":945,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130004","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00207","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公二十六年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1197\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十六年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十六年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，葬宋元公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1197\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1198\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十六年三月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十六年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，公至自齊，居于鄆。<AlignEnd Key=\"1198\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1199\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十六年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十六年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，公圍成。<AlignEnd Key=\"1199\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1200\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十六年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十六年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，公會齊侯，莒子，邾子，杞伯，盟于鄟陵，公至自會，居于鄆。<AlignEnd Key=\"1200\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1201\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十六年九月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十六年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，庚申，楚子居卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1201\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1202\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十六年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十六年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，天王入于成周，尹氏，召伯，毛伯，以王子朝奔楚。<AlignEnd Key=\"1202\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":946,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130005","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00208","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公二十七年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1203\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十七年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十七年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，公如齊，公至自齊，居于鄆。<AlignEnd Key=\"1203\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1204\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十七年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十七年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，吳弒其君僚，楚殺其大夫郤宛。<AlignEnd Key=\"1204\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1205\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十七年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十七年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，晉士鞅，宋樂祁犁，衛北宮喜，曹人，邾人，滕人，會于扈。<AlignEnd Key=\"1205\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1206\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十七年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十七年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，曹伯午卒，邾快來奔，公如齊，公至自齊，居于鄆。<AlignEnd Key=\"1206\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":947,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130006","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00209","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公二十八年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:11","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1207\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十八年三月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十八年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王三月，葬曹悼公，公如晉，次于乾侯。<AlignEnd Key=\"1207\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1208\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十八年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十八年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，丙戌，鄭伯寧卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1208\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1209\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十八年六月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十八年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，葬鄭定公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1209\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1210\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十八年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十八年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，癸巳，滕子寧卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1210\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1211\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十八年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，葬滕悼公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1211\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":948,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130007","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00210","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公二十九年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1212\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十九年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十九年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，公至自乾侯，居于鄆，齊侯使高張來唁公，公如晉，次于乾侯。<AlignEnd Key=\"1212\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1213\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十九年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十九年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，庚子，叔詣卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1213\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1214\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十九年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十九年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月。<AlignEnd Key=\"1214\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1215\" RefId=\"魯昭公二十九年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公二十九年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，鄆潰。<AlignEnd Key=\"1215\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":949,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130008","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00211","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公三十年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1216\" RefId=\"魯昭公三十年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公三十年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公在乾侯。<AlignEnd Key=\"1216\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1217\" RefId=\"魯昭公三十年六月\" Term=\"魯昭公三十年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，六月，庚辰，晉侯去疾卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1217\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1218\" RefId=\"魯昭公三十年八月\" Term=\"魯昭公三十年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月，葬晉頃公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1218\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1219\" RefId=\"魯昭公三十年十二月\" Term=\"魯昭公三十年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有二月，吳滅徐，徐子章羽奔楚。<AlignEnd Key=\"1219\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":950,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130009","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00212","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公三十一年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1220\" RefId=\"魯昭公三十一年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公三十一年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公在乾侯，季孫意如會晉荀躒於適歷。<AlignEnd Key=\"1220\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1221\" RefId=\"魯昭公三十一年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公三十一年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，丁巳，薛伯穀卒，晉侯使荀躒唁公于乾侯。<AlignEnd Key=\"1221\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1222\" RefId=\"魯昭公三十一年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公三十一年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，葬薛獻公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1222\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1223\" RefId=\"魯昭公三十一年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公三十一年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，黑肱以濫來奔。<AlignEnd Key=\"1223\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1224\" RefId=\"魯昭公三十一年十二月\" Term=\"魯昭公三十一年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，辛亥，朔，日有食之。<AlignEnd Key=\"1224\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":951,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130010","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00213","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯昭公三十二年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1225\" RefId=\"魯昭公三十二年正月\" Term=\"魯昭公三十二年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公在乾侯取闞。<AlignEnd Key=\"1225\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1226\" RefId=\"魯昭公三十二年四月\" Term=\"魯昭公三十二年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，吳伐越。<AlignEnd Key=\"1226\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1227\" RefId=\"魯昭公三十二年七月\" Term=\"魯昭公三十二年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月。<AlignEnd Key=\"1227\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1228\" RefId=\"魯昭公三十二年十月\" Term=\"魯昭公三十二年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，仲孫何忌會晉韓不信，齊高張，宋仲幾，衛世叔申，鄭國參，曹人，莒人，薛人，杞人，小邾人，城成周。<AlignEnd Key=\"1228\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1229\" RefId=\"魯昭公三十二年十二月\" Term=\"魯昭公三十二年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，己未，公薨于乾侯。<AlignEnd Key=\"1229\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":952,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130011","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00214","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯定公元年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1230\" RefId=\"魯定公元年三月\" Term=\"魯定公元年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王三月，晉人執宋仲幾于京師。<AlignEnd Key=\"1230\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1231\" RefId=\"魯定公元年六月\" Term=\"魯定公元年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，六月，癸亥，公之喪至自乾侯，戊辰，公即位。<AlignEnd Key=\"1231\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1232\" RefId=\"魯定公元年七月\" Term=\"魯定公元年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，癸巳，葬我君昭公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1232\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1233\" RefId=\"魯定公元年九月\" Term=\"魯定公元年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，大雩，立煬宮。<AlignEnd Key=\"1233\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1234\" RefId=\"魯定公元年十月\" Term=\"魯定公元年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，隕霜殺菽。<AlignEnd Key=\"1234\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":953,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130012","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00215","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯定公二年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1235\" RefId=\"魯定公二年正月\" Term=\"魯定公二年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月。<AlignEnd Key=\"1235\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1236\" RefId=\"魯定公二年五月\" Term=\"魯定公二年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月，壬辰，雉門及兩觀災。<AlignEnd Key=\"1236\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1237\" RefId=\"魯定公二年七月\" Term=\"魯定公二年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，楚人伐吳。<AlignEnd Key=\"1237\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1238\" RefId=\"魯定公二年十月\" Term=\"魯定公二年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，新作雉門及兩觀。<AlignEnd Key=\"1238\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":954,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130013","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00216","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯定公三年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1239\" RefId=\"魯定公三年正月\" Term=\"魯定公三年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公如晉，至河乃復。<AlignEnd Key=\"1239\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1240\" RefId=\"魯定公三年二月\" Term=\"魯定公三年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>二月，辛卯，邾子穿卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1240\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1241\" RefId=\"魯定公三年四月\" Term=\"魯定公三年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月。<AlignEnd Key=\"1241\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1242\" RefId=\"魯定公三年七月\" Term=\"魯定公三年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，葬邾莊公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1242\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1243\" RefId=\"魯定公三年十月\" Term=\"魯定公三年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，仲孫何忌及邾子盟于拔。<AlignEnd Key=\"1243\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":955,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130014","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00217","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯定公四年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1244\" RefId=\"魯定公四年二月\" Term=\"魯定公四年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王二月，癸巳，陳侯吳卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1244\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1245\" RefId=\"魯定公四年三月\" Term=\"魯定公四年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，公會劉子，晉侯，宋公，蔡侯，衛侯，陳子，鄭伯，許男，曹伯，莒子，邾子，頓子，胡子，滕子，薛伯，杞伯，小邾子，齊國夏，于召陵，侵楚。<AlignEnd Key=\"1245\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1246\" RefId=\"魯定公四年四月\" Term=\"魯定公四年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，庚辰，蔡公孫姓帥師滅沈，以沈子嘉歸，殺之。<AlignEnd Key=\"1246\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1247\" RefId=\"魯定公四年五月\" Term=\"魯定公四年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>五月，公及諸侯盟于皋鼬，杞伯成卒于會。<AlignEnd Key=\"1247\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1248\" RefId=\"魯定公四年六月\" Term=\"魯定公四年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，葬陳惠公，許遷于容城。<AlignEnd Key=\"1248\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1249\" RefId=\"魯定公四年七月\" Term=\"魯定公四年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，公至自會，劉卷卒，葬杞悼公，楚人圍蔡，晉士鞅衛孔圉帥師伐鮮虞，葬劉文公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1249\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1250\" RefId=\"魯定公四年十一月\" Term=\"魯定公四年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有一月，庚午，蔡侯以吳子及楚人戰于柏舉，楚師敗績，楚囊瓦出奔鄭，庚辰，吳入郢。<AlignEnd Key=\"1250\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":956,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130015","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00218","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯定公五年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1251\" RefId=\"魯定公五年三月\" Term=\"魯定公五年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王三月，辛亥，朔，日有食之。<AlignEnd Key=\"1251\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1252\" RefId=\"魯定公五年四月\" Term=\"魯定公五年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，歸粟于蔡，於越入吳。<AlignEnd Key=\"1252\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1253\" RefId=\"魯定公五年六月\" Term=\"魯定公五年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，丙申，季孫意如卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1253\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1254\" RefId=\"魯定公五年七月\" Term=\"魯定公五年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，壬子，叔孫不敢卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1254\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1255\" RefId=\"魯定公五年十月\" Term=\"魯定公五年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，晉士鞅帥師圍鮮虞。<AlignEnd Key=\"1255\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":957,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130016","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00219","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯定公六年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1256\" RefId=\"魯定公六年正月\" Term=\"魯定公六年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，癸亥，鄭游速帥師滅許，以許男歸。<AlignEnd Key=\"1256\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1257\" RefId=\"魯定公六年二月\" Term=\"魯定公六年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>二月，公侵鄭公，至自侵鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"1257\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1258\" RefId=\"魯定公六年四月\" Term=\"魯定公六年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，季孫斯，仲孫何忌，如晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"1258\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1259\" RefId=\"魯定公六年七月\" Term=\"魯定公六年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，晉人執宋行人樂祁犁。<AlignEnd Key=\"1259\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1260\" RefId=\"魯定公六年十月\" Term=\"魯定公六年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，城中城，季孫斯，仲孫忌，帥師圍鄆。<AlignEnd Key=\"1260\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":958,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130017","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00220","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯定公七年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1261\" RefId=\"魯定公七年正月\" Term=\"魯定公七年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月。<AlignEnd Key=\"1261\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1262\" RefId=\"魯定公七年四月\" Term=\"魯定公七年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月。<AlignEnd Key=\"1262\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1263\" RefId=\"魯定公七年七月\" Term=\"魯定公七年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，齊侯，鄭伯，盟于鹹，齊人執衛行人，北宮結，以侵衛，齊侯，衛侯，盟于沙，大雩，齊國夏帥師伐我西鄙。<AlignEnd Key=\"1263\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1264\" RefId=\"魯定公七年九月\" Term=\"魯定公七年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，大雩。<AlignEnd Key=\"1264\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1265\" RefId=\"魯定公七年十月\" Term=\"魯定公七年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月。<AlignEnd Key=\"1265\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":959,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130018","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00221","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯定公八年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1266\" RefId=\"魯定公八年正月\" Term=\"魯定公八年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公侵齊，公至自侵齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"1266\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1267\" RefId=\"魯定公八年二月\" Term=\"魯定公八年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>二月，公侵齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"1267\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1268\" RefId=\"魯定公八年三月\" Term=\"魯定公八年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，公至自侵齊，曹伯露卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1268\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1269\" RefId=\"魯定公八年四月\" Term=\"魯定公八年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，齊國夏帥師伐我西鄙，公會晉師于瓦，公至自瓦。<AlignEnd Key=\"1269\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1270\" RefId=\"魯定公八年七月\" Term=\"魯定公八年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，戊辰，陳侯柳卒，晉士鞅帥師侵鄭，遂侵衛，葬曹靖公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1270\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1271\" RefId=\"魯定公八年九月\" Term=\"魯定公八年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，葬陳懷公，季孫斯，仲孫何忌，帥師侵衛。<AlignEnd Key=\"1271\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1272\" RefId=\"魯定公八年十月\" Term=\"魯定公八年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，衛侯，鄭伯，盟于曲濮，從祀先公，盜竊寶玉大弓。<AlignEnd Key=\"1272\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":960,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130019","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00222","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯定公九年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1273\" RefId=\"魯定公九年正月\" Term=\"魯定公九年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月。<AlignEnd Key=\"1273\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1274\" RefId=\"魯定公九年四月\" Term=\"魯定公九年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，戊申，鄭伯蠆卒。得寶玉大弓。<AlignEnd Key=\"1274\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1275\" RefId=\"魯定公九年四月\" Term=\"魯定公九年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>得寶玉大弓。<AlignEnd Key=\"1275\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1276\" RefId=\"魯定公九年六月\" Term=\"魯定公九年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，葬鄭獻公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1276\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1277\" RefId=\"魯定公九年七月\" Term=\"魯定公九年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，齊侯，衛侯，次于五民，秦伯卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1277\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1278\" RefId=\"魯定公九年十月\" Term=\"魯定公九年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，葬秦哀公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1278\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":961,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130020","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00223","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯定公十年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1279\" RefId=\"魯定公十年三月\" Term=\"魯定公十年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王三月，及齊平。<AlignEnd Key=\"1279\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1280\" RefId=\"魯定公十年四月\" Term=\"魯定公十年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，公會齊侯于夾谷，公至自夾谷，晉趙鞅帥師圍衛，齊人來歸鄆，讙，龜陰，田，叔孫州仇，仲孫何忌，帥師圍郈。<AlignEnd Key=\"1280\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1281\" RefId=\"魯定公十年七月\" Term=\"魯定公十年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，叔孫州仇，仲孫何忌，帥師圍郈，宋樂大心出奔曹，宋公子地出奔陳。<AlignEnd Key=\"1281\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1282\" RefId=\"魯定公十年十月\" Term=\"魯定公十年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，齊侯，衛侯，鄭游速，會于安甫，叔孫州仇如齊，宋公之弟辰，暨仲佗，石彄，出奔陳。<AlignEnd Key=\"1282\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":962,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130021","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00224","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯定公十一年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1283\" RefId=\"魯定公十一年正月\" Term=\"魯定公十一年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，宋公之弟辰，及仲佗，石彄，公子地，自陳入于蕭以叛。<AlignEnd Key=\"1283\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1284\" RefId=\"魯定公十一年四月\" Term=\"魯定公十一年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月。<AlignEnd Key=\"1284\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1285\" RefId=\"魯定公十一年七月\" Term=\"魯定公十一年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，宋樂大心自曹入于蕭。<AlignEnd Key=\"1285\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1286\" RefId=\"魯定公十一年十月\" Term=\"魯定公十一年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，及鄭平，叔還如鄭蒞盟。<AlignEnd Key=\"1286\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":963,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130022","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00225","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯定公十二年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1287\" RefId=\"魯定公十二年正月\" Term=\"魯定公十二年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，薛伯定卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1287\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1288\" RefId=\"魯定公十二年四月\" Term=\"魯定公十二年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，葬薛襄公，叔孫州仇帥師墮郈，衛公孟彄帥師伐曹，季孫斯，仲孫何忌，帥師墮費。<AlignEnd Key=\"1288\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1289\" RefId=\"魯定公十二年七月\" Term=\"魯定公十二年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，大雩。<AlignEnd Key=\"1289\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1290\" RefId=\"魯定公十二年十月\" Term=\"魯定公十二年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，癸亥，公會齊侯盟于黃。<AlignEnd Key=\"1290\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1291\" RefId=\"魯定公十二年十一月\" Term=\"魯定公十二年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有一月，丙寅，朔，日有食之，公至自黃。<AlignEnd Key=\"1291\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1292\" RefId=\"魯定公十二年十二月\" Term=\"魯定公十二年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，公圍成，公至自圍成。<AlignEnd Key=\"1292\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":964,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130023","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00226","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯定公十三年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1293\" RefId=\"魯定公十三年正月\" Term=\"魯定公十三年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，齊侯，衛侯，次于垂葭。<AlignEnd Key=\"1293\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1294\" RefId=\"魯定公十三年四月\" Term=\"魯定公十三年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，築蛇淵囿，大蒐于比蒲，衛公孟彄帥師伐曹，晉趙鞅入于晉陽以叛。<AlignEnd Key=\"1294\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1295\" RefId=\"魯定公十三年十月\" Term=\"魯定公十三年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，晉荀寅，士吉射，入于朝歌以叛，晉趙鞅歸于晉，薛弒其君比。<AlignEnd Key=\"1295\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":965,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130024","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00227","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯定公十四年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1296\" RefId=\"魯定公十四年正月\" Term=\"魯定公十四年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，衛公叔戌來奔，衛趙陽出奔宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"1296\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1297\" RefId=\"魯定公十四年二月\" Term=\"魯定公十四年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>二月，辛巳，楚公子結，陳公孫佗人，帥師滅頓，以頓子牂歸。<AlignEnd Key=\"1297\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1298\" RefId=\"魯定公十四年五月\" Term=\"魯定公十四年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，衛北宮結來奔，五月，於越敗吳于檇李，吳子光卒，公會齊侯，衛侯，于牽，公至自會。<AlignEnd Key=\"1298\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1299\" RefId=\"魯定公十四年七月\" Term=\"魯定公十四年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，齊侯，宋公，會于洮，天王使石尚來歸脤，衛世子蒯瞶出奔宋，衛公孟彄出奔鄭，宋公之弟辰，自蕭來奔，大蒐于比蒲，邾子來會公，城莒父及霄。<AlignEnd Key=\"1299\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":966,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130025","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00228","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯定公十五年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1300\" RefId=\"魯定公十五年正月\" Term=\"魯定公十五年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，邾子來朝，鼷鼠食郊牛，牛死，改卜牛。<AlignEnd Key=\"1300\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1301\" RefId=\"魯定公十五年二月\" Term=\"魯定公十五年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>二月，辛丑，楚子滅胡，以胡子豹歸。<AlignEnd Key=\"1301\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1302\" RefId=\"魯定公十五年五月\" Term=\"魯定公十五年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月，辛亥郊，壬申，公薨于高寢，鄭罕達帥師伐宋，齊侯，衛侯，次于渠蒢，邾子來奔喪。<AlignEnd Key=\"1302\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1303\" RefId=\"魯定公十五年七月\" Term=\"魯定公十五年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，壬申，姒氏卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1303\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1304\" RefId=\"魯定公十五年八月\" Term=\"魯定公十五年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>八月，庚辰，朔，日有食之。<AlignEnd Key=\"1304\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1305\" RefId=\"魯定公十五年九月\" Term=\"魯定公十五年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，滕子來會葬，丁巳，葬我君定公，雨不克葬，戊午，日下吳，乃克葬，辛巳，葬定姒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1305\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1306\" RefId=\"魯定公十五年十月\" Term=\"魯定公十五年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，城漆。<AlignEnd Key=\"1306\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":967,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130026","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00229","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯哀公元年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1307\" RefId=\"魯哀公元年正月\" Term=\"魯哀公元年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，公即位，楚子，陳侯，隨侯，許男，圍蔡，鼷鼠食郊牛，改卜牛。<AlignEnd Key=\"1307\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1308\" RefId=\"魯哀公元年四月\" Term=\"魯哀公元年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，辛巳郊。<AlignEnd Key=\"1308\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1309\" RefId=\"魯哀公元年七月\" Term=\"魯哀公元年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，齊侯，衛侯，伐晉。<AlignEnd Key=\"1309\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1310\" RefId=\"魯哀公元年十月\" Term=\"魯哀公元年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，仲孫何忌帥師伐邾。<AlignEnd Key=\"1310\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":968,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130027","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00230","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯哀公二年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1311\" RefId=\"魯哀公二年二月\" Term=\"魯哀公二年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王二月，季孫斯，叔孫州仇，仲孫何忌，帥師伐邾，取漷東田及沂西田，癸巳，叔孫州仇，仲孫何忌，及邾人盟于句繹。<AlignEnd Key=\"1311\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1312\" RefId=\"魯哀公二年四月\" Term=\"魯哀公二年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，丙子，衛侯元卒，滕子來朝，晉趙鞅帥師納衛世子蒯瞶于戚。<AlignEnd Key=\"1312\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1313\" RefId=\"魯哀公二年八月\" Term=\"魯哀公二年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月，甲戌，晉趙鞅帥師，及鄭罕達帥師，戰于鐵，鄭師敗績。<AlignEnd Key=\"1313\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1314\" RefId=\"魯哀公二年十月\" Term=\"魯哀公二年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，葬衛靈公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1314\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1315\" RefId=\"魯哀公二年十一月\" Term=\"魯哀公二年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有一月，蔡遷于州來，蔡殺其大夫公子駟。<AlignEnd Key=\"1315\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":969,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130028","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00231","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯哀公三年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1316\" RefId=\"魯哀公三年正月\" Term=\"魯哀公三年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，齊國夏，衛石曼姑，帥師圍戚。<AlignEnd Key=\"1316\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1317\" RefId=\"魯哀公三年四月\" Term=\"魯哀公三年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，甲午，地震。<AlignEnd Key=\"1317\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1318\" RefId=\"魯哀公三年五月\" Term=\"魯哀公三年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>五月，辛卯，桓宮僖宮災，季孫斯，叔孫州仇，帥師城啟陽，宋樂髡帥師伐曹。<AlignEnd Key=\"1318\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1319\" RefId=\"魯哀公三年七月\" Term=\"魯哀公三年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，丙子，季孫斯卒，蔡人放其大夫公孫獵于吳。<AlignEnd Key=\"1319\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1320\" RefId=\"魯哀公三年十月\" Term=\"魯哀公三年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月，癸卯，秦伯卒，叔孫州仇，仲孫何忌，帥師圍邾。<AlignEnd Key=\"1320\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":970,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130029","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00232","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯哀公四年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1321\" RefId=\"魯哀公四年二月\" Term=\"魯哀公四年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王二月，庚戌，盜殺蔡侯申，蔡公孫辰出奔吳，葬秦惠公，宋人執小邾子。<AlignEnd Key=\"1321\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1322\" RefId=\"魯哀公四年四月\" Term=\"魯哀公四年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，蔡殺其大夫公孫姓，公孫霍，晉人執戎蠻子赤歸于楚，城西郛。<AlignEnd Key=\"1322\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1323\" RefId=\"魯哀公四年六月\" Term=\"魯哀公四年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，辛丑，亳社災。<AlignEnd Key=\"1323\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1324\" RefId=\"魯哀公四年八月\" Term=\"魯哀公四年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月，甲寅，滕子結卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1324\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1325\" RefId=\"魯哀公四年十二月\" Term=\"魯哀公四年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有二月，葬蔡昭公，葬滕頃公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1325\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":971,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130030","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00233","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯哀公五年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1326\" RefId=\"魯哀公五年正月\" Term=\"魯哀公五年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，城毗。<AlignEnd Key=\"1326\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1327\" RefId=\"魯哀公五年四月\" Term=\"魯哀公五年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，齊侯伐宋，晉趙鞅帥師伐衛。<AlignEnd Key=\"1327\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1328\" RefId=\"魯哀公五年九月\" Term=\"魯哀公五年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，九月，癸酉，齊侯杵臼卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1328\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1329\" RefId=\"魯哀公五年十月\" Term=\"魯哀公五年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，叔還如齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"1329\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1330\" RefId=\"魯哀公五年十月\" Term=\"魯哀公五年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>閏月，葬齊景公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1330\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":972,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130031","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00234","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯哀公六年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1331\" RefId=\"魯哀公六年正月\" Term=\"魯哀公六年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，城邾瑕，晉趙鞅帥師伐鮮虞，吳伐陳。<AlignEnd Key=\"1331\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1332\" RefId=\"魯哀公六年四月\" Term=\"魯哀公六年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，齊國夏及高張來奔，叔還會吳于柤。<AlignEnd Key=\"1332\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1333\" RefId=\"魯哀公六年七月\" Term=\"魯哀公六年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，庚寅，楚子軫卒，齊陽生入于齊，齊陳乞弒其君荼。<AlignEnd Key=\"1333\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1334\" RefId=\"魯哀公六年十月\" Term=\"魯哀公六年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，仲孫何忌帥師伐邾，宋向巢帥師伐曹。<AlignEnd Key=\"1334\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":973,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130032","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00235","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯哀公七年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1335\" RefId=\"魯哀公七年正月\" Term=\"魯哀公七年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，宋皇瑗帥師侵鄭，晉魏曼多帥師侵衛。<AlignEnd Key=\"1335\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1336\" RefId=\"魯哀公七年四月\" Term=\"魯哀公七年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，公會吳于鄫。<AlignEnd Key=\"1336\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1337\" RefId=\"魯哀公七年八月\" Term=\"魯哀公七年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，公伐邾，八月，己酉，入邾，以邾子益來，宋人圍曹。<AlignEnd Key=\"1337\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1338\" RefId=\"魯哀公七年十月\" Term=\"魯哀公七年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，鄭駟弘帥師救曹。<AlignEnd Key=\"1338\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":974,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130033","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00236","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯哀公八年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1339\" RefId=\"魯哀公八年正月\" Term=\"魯哀公八年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，宋公入曹，以曹伯陽歸，吳伐我。<AlignEnd Key=\"1339\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1340\" RefId=\"魯哀公八年四月\" Term=\"魯哀公八年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，齊人取讙及闡，歸邾子益于邾。<AlignEnd Key=\"1340\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1341\" RefId=\"魯哀公八年七月\" Term=\"魯哀公八年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月。<AlignEnd Key=\"1341\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1342\" RefId=\"魯哀公八年十二月\" Term=\"魯哀公八年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有二月，癸亥，杞伯過卒，齊人歸讙及闡。<AlignEnd Key=\"1342\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":975,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130034","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00237","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯哀公九年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1343\" RefId=\"魯哀公九年二月\" Term=\"魯哀公九年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王二月，葬杞僖公，宋皇瑗帥師取鄭師于雍丘。<AlignEnd Key=\"1343\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1344\" RefId=\"魯哀公九年四月\" Term=\"魯哀公九年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，楚人伐陳。<AlignEnd Key=\"1344\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1345\" RefId=\"魯哀公九年七月\" Term=\"魯哀公九年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，宋公伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"1345\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1346\" RefId=\"魯哀公九年十月\" Term=\"魯哀公九年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十月。<AlignEnd Key=\"1346\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":976,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130035","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00238","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯哀公十年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1347\" RefId=\"魯哀公十年二月\" Term=\"魯哀公十年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王二月，邾子益來奔，公會吳伐齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"1347\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1348\" RefId=\"魯哀公十年三月\" Term=\"魯哀公十年三月\"><\/AlignBegin>三月，戊戌，齊侯陽生卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1348\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1349\" RefId=\"魯哀公十年四月\" Term=\"魯哀公十年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，宋人伐鄭，晉趙鞅帥師侵齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"1349\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1350\" RefId=\"魯哀公十年五月\" Term=\"魯哀公十年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>五月，公至自伐齊，葬齊悼公，衛公孟彄自齊歸于衛，薛伯夷卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1350\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1351\" RefId=\"魯哀公十年七月\" Term=\"魯哀公十年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，葬薛惠公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1351\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1352\" RefId=\"魯哀公十年十月\" Term=\"魯哀公十年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，楚公子結帥師伐陳，吳救陳。<AlignEnd Key=\"1352\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":977,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130036","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00239","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯哀公十一年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1353\" RefId=\"魯哀公十一年正月\" Term=\"魯哀公十一年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，齊國書帥師伐我。<AlignEnd Key=\"1353\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1354\" RefId=\"魯哀公十一年四月\" Term=\"魯哀公十一年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，陳轅頗出奔鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"1354\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1355\" RefId=\"魯哀公十一年五月\" Term=\"魯哀公十一年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>五月，公會吳伐齊，甲戌，齊國書帥師及吳戰于艾陵，齊師敗績獲齊國書。<AlignEnd Key=\"1355\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1356\" RefId=\"魯哀公十一年七月\" Term=\"魯哀公十一年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，七月，辛酉，滕子虞母卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1356\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1357\" RefId=\"魯哀公十一年十一月\" Term=\"魯哀公十一年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有一月，葬滕隱公，衛世叔齊出奔宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"1357\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":978,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130037","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00240","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯哀公十二年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1358\" RefId=\"魯哀公十二年正月\" Term=\"魯哀公十二年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，用田賦。<AlignEnd Key=\"1358\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1359\" RefId=\"魯哀公十二年五月\" Term=\"魯哀公十二年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月，甲辰，孟子卒，公會吳于橐皋。<AlignEnd Key=\"1359\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1360\" RefId=\"魯哀公十二年七月\" Term=\"魯哀公十二年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，公會衛侯，宋皇瑗，于鄖，宋向巢帥師伐鄭。<AlignEnd Key=\"1360\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1361\" RefId=\"魯哀公十二年十二月\" Term=\"魯哀公十二年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有二月，螽。<AlignEnd Key=\"1361\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":979,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130038","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00241","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯哀公十三年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1362\" RefId=\"魯哀公十三年正月\" Term=\"魯哀公十三年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，鄭罕達帥師取宋師于喦。<AlignEnd Key=\"1362\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1363\" RefId=\"魯哀公十三年四月\" Term=\"魯哀公十三年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，許男成卒，公會晉侯及吳子于黃池，楚公子申帥師伐陳，於越入吳。<AlignEnd Key=\"1363\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1364\" RefId=\"魯哀公十三年七月\" Term=\"魯哀公十三年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，公至自會，晉魏曼多帥師侵衛，葬許元公。<AlignEnd Key=\"1364\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1365\" RefId=\"魯哀公十三年九月\" Term=\"魯哀公十三年九月\"><\/AlignBegin>九月，螽。<AlignEnd Key=\"1365\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1366\" RefId=\"魯哀公十三年十一月\" Term=\"魯哀公十三年十一月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，十有一月，有星孛于東方，盜殺陳夏區夫。<AlignEnd Key=\"1366\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1367\" RefId=\"魯哀公十三年十二月\" Term=\"魯哀公十三年十二月\"><\/AlignBegin>十有二月，螽。<AlignEnd Key=\"1367\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":980,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130039","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00242","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯哀公十四年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1368\" RefId=\"魯哀公十四年正月\" Term=\"魯哀公十四年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，西狩獲麟，小邾射以句繹來奔。<AlignEnd Key=\"1368\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1369\" RefId=\"魯哀公十四年四月\" Term=\"魯哀公十四年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏\u2027四月，齊陳恆執其君，寘于舒州，庚戌叔還卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1369\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1370\" RefId=\"魯哀公十四年五月\" Term=\"魯哀公十四年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>五月，庚申朔，日有食之，陳宗豎出奔楚，宋向魋入于曹以叛，莒子狂卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1370\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1371\" RefId=\"魯哀公十四年六月\" Term=\"魯哀公十四年六月\"><\/AlignBegin>六月，宋向魋自曹出奔衛，宋向巢來奔，齊人弒其君壬于舒州。<AlignEnd Key=\"1371\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1372\" RefId=\"魯哀公十四年七月\" Term=\"魯哀公十四年七月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，晉趙鞅帥師伐衛。<AlignEnd Key=\"1372\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1373\" RefId=\"魯哀公十四年八月\" Term=\"魯哀公十四年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>八月，辛丑，仲孫何忌卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1373\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1374\" RefId=\"魯哀公十四年十月\" Term=\"魯哀公十四年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，陳宗豎自楚復入于陳，陳人殺之，陳轅買出奔楚，有星孛，饑。<AlignEnd Key=\"1374\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":981,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130040","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00243","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯哀公十五年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1375\" RefId=\"魯哀公十五年正月\" Term=\"魯哀公十五年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，成叛。<AlignEnd Key=\"1375\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1376\" RefId=\"魯哀公十五年五月\" Term=\"魯哀公十五年五月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，五月，齊高無平出奔北燕，鄭伯伐宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"1376\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1377\" RefId=\"魯哀公十五年八月\" Term=\"魯哀公十五年八月\"><\/AlignBegin>秋，八月，大雩，晉趙鞅帥師伐衛。<AlignEnd Key=\"1377\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1378\" RefId=\"魯哀公十五年十月\" Term=\"魯哀公十五年十月\"><\/AlignBegin>冬，晉侯伐鄭，及齊平，衛公孟彄出奔齊。<AlignEnd Key=\"1378\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}},{"number":982,"docInfo":{"docId":"11130041","docFilename":"ChunQiu_00244","xmlFormatName":"ThdlContentXml","docXmlFormatSubname":"-","srcFilename":"_亦_銝\uf423\uefa6.xml","corpus":"春秋","corpusOrder":"1","placeInfo":[],"timeInfo":[],"docTitleXml":"<DocTitle>魯哀公十六年<\/DocTitle>","docTimeCreated":"2020-08-31 18:13:12","docContentXml":"<Content>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1379\" RefId=\"魯哀公十六年正月\" Term=\"魯哀公十六年正月\"><\/AlignBegin>春，王正月，己卯，衛世子蒯聵自戚入于衛，衛侯輒來奔。<AlignEnd Key=\"1379\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1380\" RefId=\"魯哀公十六年二月\" Term=\"魯哀公十六年二月\"><\/AlignBegin>二月，衛子還成出奔宋。<AlignEnd Key=\"1380\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<AlignBegin Type=\"Time\" Key=\"1381\" RefId=\"魯哀公十六年四月\" Term=\"魯哀公十六年四月\"><\/AlignBegin>夏，四月，己丑，孔丘卒。<AlignEnd Key=\"1381\"><\/AlignEnd>\n<\/Content>"}}],"target":"OPEN","ownerUsername":"opendb","db":"春秋三傳","corpus":"[ALL]","spotlights":"+CORPUS,文獻集,-,-","featureAnalysisSettings":"","query":".all","snippets":"off"}}